Imibare rusange y’abanduye indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19) yagiye yiyongera vuba mu bihugu by’Umuryango w'Ibihugu by'Uburayi/Akarere k’ubukungu bw’Uburayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugera kuri 15 Werurwe 2020
Imibare rusange y’abanduye indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19) iteye kimwe mu bihugu by’Umuryango w'Ibihugu by'Uburayi/Akarere k’ubukungu bw’Uburayi no mu Bwongereza bikaba byerekana ko, nubwo igeze ku rwego rutandukanye bitewe n’igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gukwirakwira vuba mu bihugu byose.
Hashingiwe ku byabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n’ahavurirwa indembe bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kwakira umubare munini w’abarwaye COVID-19 bazasabwa kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bijyanye no kwita ku barwayi barembye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa habonetse abantu barwaye umusonga watewe n’ikintu kitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko watewe na koronavirusi nshya ubu izwi nka koronavirusi ya 2 itera indwara yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva ubwo, indwara iterwa no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu ibimenyetso byerekana ko nka 80% by’abantu banduye COVID-19 bagira uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga uburwayi bwo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero bujyana cyangwa ntibujyane n’umusonga, kandi benshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi bagera kuri 14%, usanga COVID-19 ivamo indwara ikaze cyane isaba kujyanwa mu bitaro mu gihe mu barwayi basigaye bangana na 6% baremba bigasaba kwitabwaho mu byumba by’indembe.
Umubare w’abarwayi bapfa bari mu bitaro bishwe na COVID-19 ni nka 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turasuzuma uko imibare rusange y’abanduye COVID-19 ihagaze muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ibihugu by'Uburayi/Akarere k’ubukungu bw’Uburayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (UK) maze tuyigereranye n’iyo mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turanagereranya umubare w’abarwaye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK n’uwo mu Butaliyani kuva kuri 31 Mutarama kugera kuri 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abarwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y’Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu kandi usanga uko iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 gikwirakwira ahandi ku isi bigenda kimwe no muri iki gihugu.
Kuri 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi mukuru w’Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero ya Eurosurveillance 2020 yo ku wa 5 Werurwe, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje imibare y’abarwayi ba mbere bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19 i Burayi hakurikijwe igisobanuro cy’umurwayi cya OMS.
Muri EU/EEA, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye bagaragajwe n’Ubufaransa kuri 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye muri Wuhan, Intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kuva kuri 15 Werurwe 2020, mu bihugu 30 byose bigize 30 EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK) hari hatahuwe abarwaye COVID-19, ku buryo hagati y’iyi tariki na 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari hamaze kugaragara abarwayi 39 768 n’abapfuye 1 727, muri bo abarwayi 17 750 n’abapfuye 1 441 ari abo mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona umubare rusange w’abarwaye COVID-19 n’uko ikwirakirwa muri rusange
Mu Kigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara mu Burayi (ECDC), imibare y’abarwaye COVID-19 itangazwa hakurikijwe buri gihugu ku isi, yatanzwe n’ahantu hizewe gusa nka Minisiteri y’Ubuzima, inzego z’ubuzima ku rwego rw’igihugu n’akarere na OMS, igenda ivugururwa buri munsi saa 8:00.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko imibare y’abarwaye COVID-19 ihagaze muri EU/EEA na UK, no mu kuyigereranya n’iyo mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kugaragaza uko imibare y’abakirwaye COVID-19 ihagaze, twateranyije imibare y’abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, bityo twibanda ku buryo COVID-19 igenda yandura bisanzwe, muri buri gihugu kigize EU/EEA no muri UK, kuva kuri 1 Mutarama kugera kuri 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twanagaragaje imibare y’abarwayi buri gihugu cyagaragaje kuva kuri 15 Werurwe 2020 saa 8:00 tugereranyije n’iy’Ubutaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko imibare y’abarwaye COVID-19 ihagaze mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK
Muri rusange usanga uko imibare rusange y’abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK yari ihagaze mu gihe cy’iminsi 14 bimeze kimwe n’iyo mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri rusange muri EU/EEA na UK, imibare y’abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kuzamuka nko kuri 21 Gashyantare noneho izamuka bikabije nko kuri 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Inyandiko y’inyongera).
Ibi byatewe cyane cyane n’izamuka rikabije ry’umubare w’abarwayi bagaragajwe mu Butaliyani, ariko no mu bindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK hagaragaye izamuka ry’imibare y’abanduye COVID-19 (Inyandiko y’inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kirerekana ikigereranyo cy’imibare y’abarwaye COVID-19, mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK n’iyo mu Butaliyani kuva kuri 31 Mutarama kugera kuri 15 Werurwe 2020.
Cyerekana ko, kuri 15 Werurwe 8:00, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize EU/EEA na UK byari byamaze kugaragaza umubare wose w’abarwaye ungana n’uwo Ubutaliyani mu byumweru 3 mbere y’aho cyangwa uri munsi yawo.
Imyanzuro twagezeho yerekana ko umubare w’abagaragajwe ko banduye COVID-19 uzamuka vuba muri EU/EEA na UK.
Imihindagurikire y’imibare rusange y’abanduye COVID-19 yerekana ko iki cyorezo kiri gukwirakwira ku muvuduko ungana mu bihugu byose.
Ibi bikaba ari ko bimeze nubwo ibihugu biba bigeze ku bipimo bitandukanye, ingamba bifata mu rwego rw’ubuzima zikaba zihindagurika, n’ibisobanuro by’abanduye bikaba bishobora gutandukana mu bihugu ndetse hakabaho porotokore zitandukanye mu gutoranya abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo hemezwe ko barwaye COVID-19, harimo no gupima abatarabashije gupimwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe mu Butaliyani basobanuye ko abarwaye COVID-19 bagera ku 10% bari bakeneye kwitabwaho mu byumba by’indembe n’ibinyamakuru bitangaza ko ibitaro n’ahavurirwa indembe byo muri utwo turere byari byamaze kwakira umubare bidashobora kurenza.
Amakuru ku barwaye COVID-19 bashyizwe mu bitaro cyangwa ahavurirwa indembe ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ubu ni 6% na 1% by’abarwayi gusa (amakuru ntagaragazwa).
Nyamara, agomba gukusanywa mu buryo bunonosoye kugira ngo yunganire amakuru ku barwayi bakurikiranwa muri iki gihe yibanda ku mubare w’abarwayi bagaragajwe n’umubare w’abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010–11 bwerekanye ko ibyumba byakira indembe n’ibyumba byakira abarwayi batarembye cyane biboneka ku buryo butandukanye i Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29,2 mu Budage kugera kuri 4,2 ku bantu 100 000 muri Poritigali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bikeya kurusha mu Butaliyani (bari bafite ibitanda byakira indembe n’abatarembye 12,5 ku bantu 100 000 mu 2010–11).
Mu nyandiko ya gatandatu ikubiyemo amakuru mashya y’isuzuma ryihuse ry’ibibazo ECDC yakoze kuri COVID-19, hagaragaramo ingero zerekana imibare y’abarwayi irenze ubushobozi bwo kubitaho, ziherekejwe n’ikigereranyo kuri buri gihugu kigize EU/EEA na UK cy’abarwaye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro hamwe n’ikigero cya 90% cy’imibare yabo yarenga ibitanda biri ahavurirwa indembe.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu uturere tumwe na tumwe two mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK ari two dukunze kugaragaramo abarwayi benshi, kandi ibitaro n’ahavurirwa indembe usanga ubusanzwe byakira abantu bavuye mu karere kihariye, amakuru yerekeye abarwayi n’ibitanda by’indembe akwiye kuboneka ku rwego rw’ibarurishamibare ry’uturere 2 (NUTS-2).
Urugero rw’Ubutaliyani n’uko ibintu bihagaze mu bindi bihugu byerekana ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gukwirakwira vuba muri EU/EEA na UK.
Bityo, ibihugu, ibitaro n’ahavurirwa indembe bigomba kwitegura guhangana n’ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 buzakomeza mu baturage n’izamuka ry’umubare w’abarwaye COVID-19 basaba kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bijyanye no kwita ku barwayi barembye, nk’uko biri kugenda mu turere twibasiwe mu Butaliyani.
Nk’uko byavuzwe mu isuzuma ry’ibibazo ryihuse riheruka gukorwa na ECDC, ni ngombwa gukoresha uburyo rusange bwihuse kandi bukoreshwa hakiri kare mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, bityo uburyo bwo gukumira bugasimbura guma mu rugo, kubera ko izamuka ryitezwe ry’umubare w’abarwayi rishobora gutuma abafata ibyemezo n’abashinzwe ibitaro batabona umwanya uhagije wo gusesengura, kumvikana ku ngamba bagomba gufata no kuzikoresha bikwiye ziramutse zidafashwe hakiri kare.
Isuzuma ryihuse ry’ibibazo rinerekana ingamba z’ubuzima rusange zifatwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya ingaruka z’iki cyorezo.
Hari amahirwe make ibihugu byakoresha kugira ngo birusheho kongera ingamba bifata mu rwego rwo kubaganya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 n’ingaruka zayo ku nzego z’ubuzima.
Ibi biramutse bidakozwe, birashoboka ko inzego z’ubuzima zo mu bindi bihugu bigize EU/EEA byahura n’ikibazo cy’umubare munini w’abarwayi barembye mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cy’indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na koronavirusi 2 (SARS-CoV-2) itera indwara yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero ikaze cyane (SARS), imaze guhitana abantu barenga 3 000 no gufata abarenga 80 000 mu Bushinwa n’ahandi ku isi, bityo ikaba ari amakuba ku bantu.
Kimwe n’indi virusi bisa, SARS-CoV, yateye ibicurane bikaze cyane (SARS) ibihumbi by’abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na yo ishobora gukwirakwizwa n’uducurama ikaba igira ibimenyetso bisa kandi bigaragara kimwe.
Ariko COVID-19 usanga idakaze cyane kandi ihitana abantu bake ugereranyije na SARS nubwo yandura vuba cyane kandi ikaba ikunda kwibasira abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko ikanibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera umubare wiyongera cyane w’ibitangazwa kuri iyi ndwara nshya, iyi nyandiko iragerageza gukora isuzuma rusange kandi rifite akamaro ry’iyi ngingo igenda irushaho gukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Turibanda ku nshoza z’ibanze nk’ubumenyi bw’iyi ndwara, ikiyitera, virusi iyitera, uko isuzumwa, uko ivurwa, uko ikwirakwira n’uko yirindwa.
Nubwo hakiri ibibazo byinshi bisaba gusubizwa, twizeye ko iri suzuma rizafasha mu kumenya no kurandura iyi ndwara ibangamiye ubuzima.
Iserukiramuco (Spring Festival) ryo ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 rimaze kwandika amateka adashobora kwibagirana mu Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma iwabo mu biruhuko byose no mu byumweru byinshi byakurikiyeho bitewe n’icyorezo cyatewe na virusi nshya.
Iyi virusi ifite ibintu byinshi ihuriyeho na koronavirusi (CoV) yateye icyorezo cy’ibicurane bikaze cyane (SARS) mu 2003; bityo Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) rikaba ryarayise SARS-CoV-2 ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, noneho indwara iyikomokaho yitwa Indwara ya CoV 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu Bushinwa, nuko gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, abantu barenga 80 000 bari bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye virusi ya COVID-19, muri bo abarenga 40 000 bamaze gusezererwa naho abapfuye barenga 3 000.
OMS iburira abantu yemeza ko COVID-19 ari “umwanzi rusange wa 1” kandi ko ishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk’uko bigaragazwa na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, hatangajwe inyandiko zirenga 200 kuri COVID-19 harimo izivuga kuri virusi iyitera, ku cyorezo cyayo, aho yakomotse, uko isuzumwa n’uko ivurwa kuva igihe raporo ya mbere yatangarijwe ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yasobanuye imiterere ya virusi yari yafashwe mu barwayi batandukanye.
Iri suzuma riragerageza gukora incamake y’ubushakashatsi bumaze gukorwa kuri iyi ngingo nshya kandi irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi cyane.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tuzagerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS ndetse n’indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, nk’ibicurane byo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, byagaragaye mu 2012).
Tuzanasuzuma amasomo tumaze kunguka kugeza ubu ku bijyanye no gukumira ikwirakirwa no kumenya igitera iyi ndwara ndetse na bimwe mu bibazo byihutirwa bitarabonerwa ibisubizo.
Virusi zo mu bwoko bwa CoVs ubasanzwe zifatwa nka virusi zitica abantu, usanga zitera cyane cyane ubwoko 4 bw’ibicurane bikunze kuboneka ku gipimo kigera nko kuri 15%.
Ariko, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na virusi za CoVs zibasira abantu cyane incuro ebyiri, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zateye icyorezo cyagaragaye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite 2012, noneho nyuma yaho zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi abantu batagira ingano barandura abandi barapfa.
Ni yo mpamvu COVID-19 yo muri iyi minsi ari icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV kigaragaye mu mateka ya muntu.
Nk’uko bigaragara mu Gishushanyo ​Igishushanyo cya 1.1, abantu barwaye umusonga watewe n’ikintu kitazwi bagaragaye bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 ari na bwo byamenyeshejwe Komisiyo y’Igihugu Ishinzwe Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y’iminsi irindwi ni bwo hasohotse inyandiko isobanura imiterere ya CoV.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020 ni bwo hapfuye umuntu wa mbere muri Wuhan.
Hagati aho icyorezo cyakwirakwiye vuba mu yindi mijyi, intara n’ibihugu bituranye.
Kuri 20 Mutarama, hatangajwe ko hari abaganga banduye, byumvikana ko abantu bashobora kwanduzanya iyi virusi.
Kuri 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe mu kato n’uburyo bwose bwo gutwara abantu burahagarikwa.
Kuri 24 Mutarama ni bwo ubushakashatsi bw’ubuvuzi bwa mbere kuri iyi ndwara bwatangaje ko, mu barwayi 41 bari bemejwe ko banduye, 21 ni bo bonyine bari bageze ku isoko ry’ibituruka mu nyanja ry’i Wuhan abantu bavugaga ko ari ho ubwandu bwari bwaturutse butewe n’inyamaswa itazwi.
Kuri 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari amakuba abangamiye ubuzima ku isi.
Igihe iyi raporo yatangazwaga, iyi ndwara yari yamaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo ​(Igishushanyo cya 2).2).
Kubera iki cyorezo kiri gukwirakwira vuba, ntibyoroshye kumenya aho kizagarukira n’ingaruka zacyo.
Kuri 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku bigo binyuranye ku barwayi 8 866 barimo abarwayi 4 021 bagaragajwe ko banduye COVID-19 bwatanze ishusho ivuguruye kurushaho y’uko iki cyorezo gihagaze dusanga ku rubuga (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 bafite imyaka inyuranye, ariko biganjemo abafite hagati y’imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi icya kabiri (47,7%) cy’abanduye bari barengeje imyaka 50, bake cyane bafite munsi ya 20, noneho abantu banduye 14 gusa bari bafite munsi y’imyaka 10.
Abagabo ni bo banduye SARS-CoV-2 cyane (0,31/100 000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100 000).
COVID-19 yakwirakwiye cyane cyane muri Hubei no mu turere byegeranye.
Ugereranyije, kuva COVID-19 yagaragara kugera habonetse uburyo isuzumwa hashize nk’iminsi 5 (2-9).
Ugereranyije byafashe iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) kugira ngo igaragaze ibimenyetso.
Ugereranyije umuntu wa mbere yapfuye hashize 9,5 (4,8-13) kuva igaragaye.
Umubare w’ibanze w’abashobora kwandura (R0) wari 3,77 (95% CI: 3,51-4,05), naho R0 iburungushuye yari 2,23-4,82.
Umubare w’abanduye wiyongeye bikabije mbere yo kuri 23 Mutarama 2020, uhura n’igihe abantu benshi baba bakora ingendo mbere y’iserukiramuco ‘Spring Festival’ mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w’abemejwe ko banduye wari 1,44% (95% CI: 1,10-1,86%), naho umubare uburungushuye w’abapfa mu barwayi bose wari 3,06% (95% CI: 2,02-4,59%).
Ibibazo bitatu bikomeye kuri COVID-19 byari igitsina (gabo), imyaka (≥60), n’umusonga ukaze.
Virusi za CoVs ni akaryango ka virusi nini zifite utwugara zirimo RNA y’ibyiyumviro imwe rukumbi.
Zishobora gushyirwa mu bwoko bune, ari bwo alufa, beta, gama na delita. Muri ubu bwoko virusi za CoVs zo mu bwoko bwa alufa na beta ni zo zishobora kwanduza abantu.
Girikoporoteyine yo ku mutwe (S) w’akugara ifata ku imvubura bita ACE2 n’indi bita DPP4 mu gihe cya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, noneho ingenangingo zikihuza.
Jenome ya virusi ya RNA iravuburwa ikajya mu y’ingirabuzimafatizo; jenome ya virusi yamara gukopororwa, RNA ya jenome iri kumwe na girikoporoteyine z’akugara na poroteyine za nekereyokapuside ikora imvubura z’inyangingo fatizo zihuza n’ingenangingo za purasima zikavamo virusi.
Imiterere ya mbere ya jenome ya SARS-CoV-2 yagaragajwe ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
Hagaragaye ko SARS-CoV-2 ari ubwoko bushya bwa beta-CoV byahuje jene ku kigero cya 99,98% mu bizamini ndangamiterere 10 byafashwe aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, mu isoko ry’ibiva mu nyanja ry’i Huanan muri Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite jene zisa cyane n’iza SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Muri mikorosikope ya elegitoronike isuzuma uko yandura, uduce twa SARS-CoV-2 twagaragaye mu bice binanutse bikabije bya epiteriyumu y’imyanya y’ubuhumekero y’umuntu.
Imvubura ya ACE2 mu muntu ni yo basanze ibamo SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV.
Ariko poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 yihuza n’imvubura ya ACE2 y’umuntu buhoro cyane kurusha iya SARS-CoV, ibi bikaba bihuye n’ibyemezwa ko SARS-CoV-2 yanduza abarwayi bidakabije kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kuba poroteyine ngufi nshya ikorwa na poroteyine ya orf3b na poroteyine ivuburwa ikorwa na poroteyine ya orf8.
Poroteyine ya orf3b yo muri SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba igira uruhare mu bushobozi bwo gutera indwara bwa virusi no kubuza IFNβ kugaragara; ariko poroteyine ya orf8 ntabwo ibamo imiterere cyangwa imimerere izwi.
Ku itariki ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou na bagenzi be batangaje imiterere yo muri mikorosikope ya elegitoronike ikoresha ubushyuhe bwo hasi cyane (cryo-EM) bw’imvubura ya ACE2 yuzuye y’umuntu ku bucucike bwa 2,9 Å mu rusobe rw’inyangingo igendamo aside amino B0AT1.
Basanze ko urwo rusobe, rufite imiterere ifunguye n’ifunze, yikusanyije nk’inyangingo ebyiri kandi urusobe rwa ACE2-B0AT1 rushobora guhuza poroteyine za S ebyiri, bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy’imigaragarire n’ubwandu bya virusi ya CoV.
B0AT1 ishobora kwibandwaho mu gusuzuma imiti yo kurandura ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Inyamaswa yakomotseho n’iyandujwe bwa mbere
Birazwi ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zombi zaturutse mu ducurama noneho abantu bakazanduzwa n’impimbi n’ingamiya.
Hifashishijwe igereranyankomoko rya SARS-CoV-2 hamwe n’izindi virusi za CoVs, byagaragaye ko uducurama ari two SARS-CoV-2 yakomotseho kubera ko virusi nshya iteye kimwe ku kigero cya 96% na virusi ebyiri za CoVs zisa nka SARS zikomoka ku ducurama zitwa ‘bat-SL-CoVZX45’ na ‘bat-SL-CoVZX21’.
Ariko inyamaswa yanduye bwa mbere yafashije iyi virusi kubasha kwibasira ubwoko bunyuranye kugeza yanduje abantu ntiramenyekana, kandi n’uburyo yanduramo ntiburamenyekana neza.
Ji na bagenzi be bavuze ko inzoka zishobora kuba ari zo zanduje abantu iyi virusi ziyandujwe n’uducurama bikaba byarajyanye no kwiyuburura muri poroteyine ya S.
Nk’uko bigaragazwa n’ubushakashatsi, abashakashatsi bo muri Guangzhou, mu Bushinwa, bavuze ko ibisamujyonjyo, inyamabere zigira umunwa muremure zirya intozi zikaba zikoreshwa cyane n’abavuzi ba gihanga mu Bushinwa, bishobora kuba ari byo byanduye bwa mbere SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n’imiterere ya jene iteye kimwe ku kigero cya 99% yatahuwe muri virusi ya CoV yo mu bisamujyonjyo na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, ikinyuranyo cya 1% kigaragara muri jenome zombi kiracyari kinini; bityo hategerejwe imyanzuro itanga ibimenyetso bifatika (Igishushanyo ​(Igishushanyo 33).
Ibyinshi mu biranga virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ntibiramenyekana.
Virusi za SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kumara hanze amasaha 48 ziri ahantu hashyushye, zikaba zageza ku minsi 5 ziri ahantu hafite ubushyuhe buri munsi ya 20 °C n’ubuhehere buri hagati ya 40% na 50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira ibiyiranga bimwe.
Hagaragajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 itihanganira imirasire y’izuba n’ubushyuhe bwo kuri dogere 56 °C mu minota 30; eteri, etanoru 75%, imiti bisukuza irimo korore, aside perasetike, kororoforume, n’ibindi bitembabuzi by’amavuta, ariko atari kororegisidine, bishobora kwica iyi virusi neza.
Muri rusange abantu bose nta budahangarwa bagira kuri SARS-CoV-2 bityo baka bibasirwa n’iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse burakorwa ku byerekeranye n’uko umubiri uhangana na SARS-CoV-2.
Ni yo mpamvu, twifashisha gusa ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi virusi za CoV, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo ​(Igishushanyo cya 4).4).
Muri rusange, iyo virusi imaze kwinjira mu wayanduye, ibanza gutahurwa n’ubudahangarwa kamere binyuze mu nyakira zitandukanya imisusire (PRR) zikubiyemo inyakira zimeze nka regitine zo mu bwoko bwa C, inyakira ya TLR, inyakira ya NLR n’inyakira ya RLR.
Mu nzira zinyuranye, iyi virusi itera ubushye, kubyimba kw’uturemangingo ngaragira, no kwiyegeranya kwa poroteyine zo mu bwoko bwa I (IFN) ziremwa mu rwego rwo guhangana na virusi bigabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi maze bikongera kuribwa kwa virusi zateye indwara.
Ariko, poroteyine ya N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha iyi virusi gucika ibiyirwanya by’ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri.
Nyuma y’igihe gito, ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri butangira kurwanya iyi virusi.
Ingirabuzima fatizo za T zikubiyemo uturemangingo twa CD4+ na CD8+ T tugira uruhare rukomeye mu kurinda umubiri.
Uturemangingo twa CD4+ T twongerera imbaraga uturemangingo twa B kugira ngo dukore abasirikare b’umubiri bashobora guhangana n’iyo virusi, noneho uturemangingo twa CD8+ T tugahita twica uturemangingo twanduye virusi.
Uturemangingo dufasha twa T dukora sitokine zifasha gutwika kugira ngo zifashe kurinda uturemangingo.
Ariko CoV ishobora guca intege imikorere y’uturemangingo twa T itera urupfu rw’uturemangingo twa T.
Ubudahangarwa bwo mu matembabuzi bukubiyemo inyunganira nka C3a na C5a n’abasirikare b’umubiri na bwo bugira akamaro mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare b’umubiri bavanwe mu murwayi wakize baciye intege MERS-CoV.
Ikindi kandi, kwirwanaho bikabije by’ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri bituma habaho umubare munini w’ingengangingo zidafite aho zifashe mu mubiri zishobora gutuma ibihaha n’izindi ngingo byangirika cyane, noneho, byagenda nabi, ingingo zinyuranye zikareka gukora hakaba hanavamo n’urupfu.
Ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, bwagaragaye mu banduye igitangira, ikunda kwibasira abantu bashaje barwaye izindi ndwara zinyuranye n’abagore batwite.
Akenshi usanga abantu bibasiwe na virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri budakora neza ari bo baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura kurusha abandi.
Ikigereranyo cy’iminsi SARS-CoV-2 imara mu mubiri mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni hagati y’iminsi 1 na 14, akenshi akaba ari hagati y’iminsi 3 na 7 hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 425 ba mbere muri Wuhan.
Ariko, ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 1 099 bwerekanye ko igihe bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare ari iminsi 3 muri rusange kandi ko kiba hagati y’iminsi 0 na 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwa vuba cyane, nk’uko byavuzwe haruguru, bwerekanye ko igihe bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare ari iminsi 4,8 (3,0-7,2) hashingiwe ku mubare w’abarwayi 8 866.
Ni ngombwa cyane ko inzego z’ubuzima zagena igihe cy’akato kiboneye hashingiwe ku gihe nyacyo bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare kurusha ibindi, bityo bikaba byabuza abantu banduye ariko badafite ibimenyetso kwanduza abandi.
Nk’uko bisanzwe, abantu bahuye n’ubwandu cyangwa banduye virusi basabwa kujya mu kato k’iminsi 14.
Igihe cy’akato kiramutse cyongewe kikagera ku minsi 24?
Akenshi umuriro ni cyo kimenyetso gikomeye cya mbere cya COVID-19, ukaba ushobora kutajyana n’ikindi kimenyetso cyangwa ukajyana n’ibindi bimenyetso nk’inkorora y’akayi, guhumeka bigoranye, kuribwa mu ngingo, isereri, umutwe, kuribwa mu muhogo, ibicurane byinshi, kuribwa mu gatuza, impiswi, iseseme no kuruka.
Hari abarwayi bahumetse bigoranye cyangwa bagira ogisijeni nke mu maraso nyuma y’icyumweru bamaze gufatwa n’indwara.
Abarwayi barembye bahise bagira ibibazo bikomeye bwo guhumeka, umuvuduko w’amaraso wo hasi, ibibazo by’aside yo mu mubiri n’ibyo kuvura kw’amaraso.
Abarwari bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero n’umuriro ukaze, nubwo baba nta bibazo by’ibihaha baba bagaragaza, bagomba gukorerwa ikizamini cya virusi hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi ku byiciro by’abarwayi bwakozwe mu mpera z’Ukuboza mu 2019 bwagaragaje ko ijanisha ry’ibimenyetso ryari 98% ku muriro, 76% ku nkorora y’akayi, 55% ku bibazo bya ogisijeni na 3% ku mpiswi; 8% ku barwayi basabye imashini zibafasha guhumeka.
Imyanzuro nk’iyi yatanzwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buheruka gukorwa ku banduriye mu miryango no ku bandujwe n’abantu badafite ibimenyetso.
Kimwe n’ubu bushakashatsi, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 ku banduye bwerekanye ko abarwaye MERS-CoV na bo bagize umuriro (98%), inkorora y’akayi (47%) n’ibibazo bya ogisijeni (55%) nk’ibimenyetso by’ibanze.
Ariko 80% muri bo basabye imashini zibafasha guhumeka kurusha mu barwaye COVID-19 n’umubare w’abapfuye uba munini kuri MERS kurusha uwa COVID-19.
Impiswi (26%) no kubabara mu muhogo (21%) na byo byagaragaye mu barwaye MERS.
Mu barwaye SARS, hagaragaye ko umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora y’akayi (29%-75%), ibibazo bya ogisijeni (40%-42%), impiswi (20-25%) no kubabara mu muhogo (13-25%) ari byo bimenyetso bikomeye n’abarwayi basabye imashini zibafasha guhumeka bageze nko kuri 14%-20%.
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, ijanisha ry’abishwe na COVID-19 ryari 2% igihe abarwayi bemejwe ku isi bari 66 576.
Kimwe no kuri iyi virusi, ijanisha ry’abishwe na SARS ryari 10% by’abarwayi bemejwe 8 096 mu Ugushyingo 2002.
Kuri MERS, hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw’abanduye bwo muri Kamena 2012, ijanisha ry’abapfuye ryari 37% by’abarwayi bemejwe 2 494.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere y’aho bwagaragaje ko umubare w’ibanze w’abandura (R0) SARS-CoV-2 wari uhanitse ungana na 6,47, ikigereranyo cy’abandura kuri 95% (CI) ari 5,71-7,23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4 gusa.
Igereranya rya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV ku byerekeranye n’ibimenyetso, umubare w’abapfa na R0 turarisanga mu mbonerahamwe ​Imbonerahamwe 1.1.
Imibare imaze kuvugwa yerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi buhanitse bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ikaba yica abantu bake kurusha izo zindi.
Ni yo mpamvu bikomeye cyane kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kurusha icya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi abandura bagaragara mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu iteraniro cyangwa imodoka imwe nk’ubwato batemberamo.
Akenshi abarwayi baba barigeze gutemberera cyangwa gutura mu ntara ya Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi turere twibasiwe cyangwa se barahuye n’abantu banduye cyangwa barwaye mu byumweru bibiri byabanjirije igihe bafatiwe.
Ariko, byagaragaye ko abantu bashobora kugendana n’iyi virusi nta bimenyetso bafite mu gihe kirenga ibyumweru bibiri kandi ko abarwayi bakize bagasezererwa mu bitaro bashobora kuba bagifite iyi virusi, bikaba byerekana ko ari ngombwa kongera igihe cy’akato.
Abarwayi bagira umubare usanzwe cyangwa muke w’uturemangingo tw'umweru two mu maraso (cyane cyane ingirabuzima fatizo) mu minsi ya mbere.
Urugero, umubare muto w’ingirabuzima fatizo mu turemangingo tw'umweru two mu maraso ni &lt; 4×109/L harimo ingirabuzima fatizo &lt; 1×109/L, naho ibipimo byo hejuru by’asiparitate aminotaransiferaze (AST) na virusi ziboneka mu maraso byabonetse mu barwaye COVID-19 bangana na 1 099.
Ibipimo by’imvubura z’umwijima n’imikaya na miyogorobine byiyongeye mu maraso y’abarwayi bamwe na bamwe, no kwirundanya kwa poroteyine zikorwa n’umwijima na eritirosite kwariyongeye mu maraso y’abarwayi benshi.
Abarwayi barembye, igipimo cya D-dima, imvubura iterwa no kwangirika kwa fibirine iboneka mu maraso, cyari kiri hejuru, n’umubare w’ingirabuzima fatizo wagiye ugabanuka.
Ibibazo bigaragara mu kunyuza agatuza mu cyuma biboneka mu barweye COVID-19 benshi kandi bigaragazwa n’ibicucu biremekanye mu mpande zombi cyangwa ubwijime bwereruka (GGO) bw’ibihaha.
Akenshi abarwayi bagira umusonga udasanzwe, ibisebe kibaze mu bihaha n’ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka (ARDS).
Iyo habayeho ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka (ARDS), ubushye bukabije, kwirundanya kw’amatembabuzi n’ibihaha bigenda bibabuka bibangamira cyane ihererekanwa ry’umwuka.
Kudakora kwa pinemosite zo mu bwoko bwa I na II bigabanya igipimo cy’utunyangingo tugabanya umwanya hagati y’amatembabuzi no bigatuma ingingo zirushaho kubyigana, bityo bikagabanya ubushobozi bw’ibihaha bwo kwikwedura noneho bikongera ibyago byo gutuma ibihaha bireka gukora.
Ni yo mpamvu, ibisubizo bibi bya radiyo y’agatuza akenshi usanga bijyana n’ubukare bukabije bw’iyi ndwara.
Kuri 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry’igitera COVID-19 ryagaragaje ishishuka rya pinemosite, kubyimba kw’ingenangingo z’ibihaha, icengera ry’ingirabuzima fatizo mu myanya y’umwuka, n’uturemangingo dukomatanye dufite intima nyinshi mu bihaha by’umurwayi wishwe n’iyi ndwara, bihuye n’inkomoko ry’ubwandu bwa virusi n’ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka (ARDS), bikanamera kimwe no mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Itahurwa rya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 RNA hifashishijwe uburyo bwo muri raboratwari bwa RT-PCR ryakoreshejwe nk’ikigenderwaho cy’ibanze mu isuzumwa rya COVID-19.
Ariko, kubera igipimo gihanitse cy’ibisubizo bivuga ko umuntu atanduye atari ukuri, bishobora gutuma icyorezo kirushaho gukwirakwira, ibimenyetso byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma (bitacyibanda gusa ku buryo bwa RT-PCR) mu Bushinwa kuri 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibi ni ko byanagenze ku isuzumwa rya SARS.
Ni yo mpamvu gukomatanya amateka y’indwara, ibimenyetso, ibizamini byo muri raboratwari n’ibisubizo byo kunyura mu cyuma bifite akamaro kandi bikaba na ngombwa kugira ngo hakorwe isuzuma riboneye.
Kuri 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda riyobowe na Feng Zhang ryasobanuye porotokore yo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingira kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, itahura ibice by’ibyiganano bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 ku rugero rwa 20 × 10-18 mol/L kugera kuri 200 × 10-18 mol/L (kopi 10-100 kuri mikorolitiro cy’ibyinjijwe) hakoreshejwe igipimo cy’amavutta mu gihe kitageze ku isaha bidasabye ibikoresho bihambaye.
Hari icyizere ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kuzamura cyane ireme buramutse bugenzuwe mu bizamini byo kwa muganga.
Kubera kutamenyera CoV nshya, abaganga bashobora mbere na mbere kuba hafi y’abarwaye COVID-19, mu gihe barimo kugerageza imiti inyuranye yatanzwe cyangwa yifujwe mbere yo kuvura izindi CoVs nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n’izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe ​(Imbonerahamwe ya 2).2).
Iyi miti ibamo imiti ikoreshwa n’ishobora gukoreshwa hamwe n’imiti irwanya virusi, imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri, imiti igabanya kubyimba, purazima yavanwe mu barwayi bakize, imiti y’Abashinwa, n’ubufasha nsanamutima.
Hanifujwe ko purazima yavanwe mu barwayi bakize yakoreshwa mu kuvura virusi.
Amasosiyete akora imiti ari gukora atikoresheje kugira ngo akore abasirikare b’umubiri n’inkingo zihangana n’iyi virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha igitangira noneho ikaba ishobora no kwibasira, ku rugero rwo hasi, izindi ngingo zikora ACE2 nk’urwungano ngongozi n’impyiko.
Nyamara, gukora nabi no kudakora by’imyanya y’ubuhumekero ni byo bibazo bibangamira ubuzima bw’abarwayi n’impamvu nyamukuru y’urupfu.
Ni yo mpamvu ubufasha bwo guhumeka ari ingenzi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora abantu kandi hakaba harimo no kongerera umwuka muri rusange, kongerera umwuka ku gipimo cyo hejuru, gushyira ku mashini ifasha guhumeka bidakabije no guhumekera ku mashini ifasha guhumeka bitewe n’ubukare bw’indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by’ibabazo byo guhumeka bikomeye bagomba kunganirwa n’uburyo bwo kongerera umwuka bwa ECMO, uburyo busimbura inzira y’ubuhumekero yo mu mutima n’ibihaha bukoreshwa mu kuvura abafite ibibazo bikomeye by’umutima cyangwa byo guhumeka.
Ikindi, kwita ku mikorere y’impyiko, kurwanya no kuvura izindi ndwara n’umuvuduko w’amaraso wo hasi, kubungabunga imikorere y’ingingo z’ingenzi na byo bigirira akamaro abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Birazwi ko ubwiyongere bwa sitokine buterwa no kwirwanaho bikabije by’ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Ubwiyongere bwa sitokine ni uburyo bw’igisubizo cyo kwikingira cy’urwungano kigaragazwa no kuvubura sitokine zinyuranye nka TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi sitokine zituma uturemangingo tw’ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri turekura umubare munini w’ingengangingo zidafite aho zifashe akaba ari zo zitera cyane cyane ARDS no kureka gukora kw’ingingo zinyuranye.
Kugabanya ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri bigira akamaro mu kuvura ubwiyongere bwa sitokine, cyane cyane mu barwayi barembye.
Korutikositeroyide na tosilizumabe, umusirikare w’umubiri ufite korone imwe urwanya IL6, zakoreshejwe mu kuvura ubwiyongere bwa sitokine.
Iyindi miti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri mu kuvura ubwiyongere bwa sitokine irimo kugabanya ingufu z’ubwirinzi bw’umubiri bwibasira uturemangingo twa T; gukumira IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; guca intege JAK; birinatumomabe; igabanya ry’ibimenyetso bya sitokine 4; n’imiti ica intege HDAC.
Imiti igabanya kubyimba, nk’imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri, yakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukare bw’ingaruka z’ubwirinzi bw’umubiri.
Ariko, gufata imiti igabanya kubyimba myinshi nta kamaro byagize ku bihaha byacitse ibisebe bikaze mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo ishobora gutera ibibazo bikomeye, cyane cyane indwara y’amagufa (AVN), bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku mivurirwe y’indwara.
Nyamara, hifujwe ko doze nke n’izo mu rugero za korutikositeroyide zahabwa abarwayi ba COVID-19 barembye cyane mu gihe gito kandi bigakoranwa ubushishozi.
Igihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, mu muntu uboneye urwanya virusi wari wakabonetse.
Ariko gutera urushinge rwa remdesivir, iteye kimwe na nikerewotide, byagaragaye ko bifite akamaro mu Munyamerika urwaye COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti urwanya virusi mushya wakozwe na Gilead ugenewe kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi za Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma y’aho, remdesivir na yo yaje kugaragaza ko ishobora guca intege izindi virusi zigizwe na RNA zirimo virusi za MERS na SARS.
Hashingiwe ku bimaze kuvugwa, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uyu muti kugira ngo bukore ubushakashatsi bubiri ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, abantu bakaba bategereje cyane icyo bizatanga.
Ikindi kandi, umuti wa baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin yagaragajwe ko ishobora kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by’ibibazo byo guhumeka bikomeye.
Impiswi, iseseme, kuruka, kwangiriza kw’umwijima n’ibindi bibazo bikomeye bishobora kubaho bitewe no gukomatanya imiti na lopinavir/ritonavir.
Imikoranire y’iyi miti n’iyindi miti ikoreshwa mu barwayi igomba gukurikiranwa neza.
Purazima yavanwe mu barwayi bakize n’ikorwa ry’abasirikare b’umubiri
Gufata amaraso y’abantu bakize indwara yanduza mu rwego rwo kuyavuza abandi barwaye indwara imwe cyangwa kurinda abantu batarwaye kwandura iyo ndwara bimaze igihe kirekire bikorwa.
Ni byo koko, abarwayi bakize akenshi baba bafite umubare ugihe kuba munini w’abasirikare b’umubiri barwanya virusi iri mu maraso yabo.
Abasirikare b’umubiri ni gorobirine irinda umubiri indwara (Ig) ikorwa n’ingirabuzima fatizo za B kugira ngo irwanye virusi n’ibindi bintu bidasanzwe bakaba bamenya morekire rukumbi zo muri virusi noneho bagahita bazica.
Hashingiwe ku bimaze kuvugwa, purazima yavanwa mu maraso y’itsinda ry’abarwayi bakize COVID-19 noneho aterwa mu barwayi barembye cyane 10.
Ibimenyetso bari bafite byatangiye koroha mu masaha 24, bijyana n’igabanyuka ry’ububyimbe n’umubare wa virusi ndetse na ogusijene iriyongera mu maraso.
Ariko igenzura n’isobanura ni ngombwa kugira ngo hatangwe uburyo bwo kuyakoresha mu barwayi benshi mu gihe hatarakorwa imiti yihariye.
Ikindi kandi, kubera ingaruka z’imiti, zimwe mu ngaruka mbi zijyana na purazima zigomba gusuzumwana ubushishozi.
Urugero, abasirikare b’umubiri bashobora kongera bikabije ubwirinzi bw’umubiri noneho bigatuma hakorwa sitokine, zishobora kuba uburozi bwashyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Ubusanzwe abasirikare b’umubiri aba ari bake mu maraso kandi hasabwa purazima nyinshi mu kuvura abarwayi barembye cyane.
Ntibyoroshye gukora abasirikare b’umubiri bihariye vuba bihagije mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo mpuzamahanga.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ngombwa kandi bikabi bikwiye kuvana uturemangingo twa B mu barwayi bakize noneho hagashakwamo kode za jene zigize abasirikare b’umubiri bakaze cyangwa gusuzuma abasirikare b’umubiri bakaze bagereranywa na poroteyine za ngombwa zigize iyo virusi.
Bigenze gutyo, twabasha rwose kongera ikorwa ry’abasirikare b’umubiri.
Hashize imyaka ibihumbi n’ibihumbi ubuvuzi gakondo bw’Abashinwa (TCM) bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zinyuranye mu Bushinwa.
Ariko imikorere yayo ishingira cyane ku gukomatanya imiti inyuranye mu buryo buhindagurika bitewe n’isuzuma ry’indwara hashingiwe ku buryo bukoreshwa muri TCM.
Imyinshi mu miti igira akamaro ntiramenyekana cyangwa ntizwi neza kubera ko bikomeye kuyiyungurura no kugenzura iyo miti cyangwa ibipimo by’imivangirwe yayo.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ibura ry’umuti wihariye uvura COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti ikomeye yunganira abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje n’ibyo mu rugero cyangwa abarwayi bamaze koroherwa.
Urugero, ibitonyanga bya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen byagaragaye ko bishobora kugira akamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byo hejuru byo gukira mu kuvura abarwaye COVID-19 byagaragaye mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM muri 87% by’abarwayi baho, nko muri Gansu (63,7%), Ningxia (50%) no muri Hunan (50%), naho mu ntara ya Hubei, yakoresheje TCM nko muri 30% gusa by’abarwaye COVID-19, habonetseyo igipimo cyo gukira cyo hasi cyane (13%).
Ariko iri ni igereranya ridacukumbuye kubera ko ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka nk’umubare no kuremba by’abarwayi bigomba kwitabwaho mu isuzuma.
Kuri 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang n’abo bakorana batangaje ubushakashatsi bugereranya kuvura bakoresha imiti y’i Burayi no muri Amerika yonyine no kuvura bakomatanya WM na TCM.
Basanze ibihe bisabwa kugira ngo umubiri usubirane ubushyuhe busanzwe, ibimenyetso bikire no kugira ngo umuntu ashyirwe mu bitaro ari bigufi cyane mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM gusa.
Icyashimishije cyane ni uko igipimo cyo gukomera kw’ibimenyetso (kuva ku bimenyetso byoroheje kugera ku bikaze) cyagabanyutse bigaragara mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM gusa (7,4% kuri 46,2%) n’umubare w’abapfa wabaye muto mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda ry’abahawe WM gusa (8,8% kuri 39%).
Nyamara, akamaro n’ubuziranenge bya TCM biracyategereje gukorwaho ubushakashatsi bunonosoye kurushaho ku bantu benshi no mu bigo byinshi.
Byanaba byiza kugaragaza uko iyi miti ikora no gusobanura neza ibigize imiti ya TCM bigira akamaro ikoreshejwe yonyine cyangwa ikomatanyijwe n’iyindi biramutse bishoboka.
Abarwayi bakekwa cyangwa bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 akenshi usanga bagira ubwoba bwinshi bwo kuba iyi ndwara yandura cyane ikaba yanabaviramo gupfa, n’abashyirwa mu kato na bo usanga batabyakira neza, bumva bari bonyine bikanabatera kurakara.
Na none, ibimenyetso by’ubwandu nk’umuriro, ibibazo by’umwuka muke, inkorora n’ingaruka mbi z’imiti nko kubura ibitotsi biterwa na korutikositeroyide bishobora gutuma umuntu agira umuhangayiko mwinshi n’ibibazo byo mu mutwe.
Mu ntangiriro z’icyorezo cya SARS, habonetse ibibazo binyuranye byo mu mutwe birimo ihungabana rihoraho, umuhangayiko, kugira ubwoba, gucanganyikirwa, guta ubwenge, guta umutwe, no gushaka kwiyahura.
Gushakashaka abantu umuntu yahuye na bo no gushyirwa mu kato ku itegeko bikorwa mu rwego rw’ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 zifatwa n’inzego z’ubuzima za Leta, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika no kwicira urubanza ku bijyanye n’ingaruka zo kwandura, akato n’ivangura ku miryango n’inshuti zabo.
Ni yo mpamvu serivisi z’ubuzima bwo mu mutwe zigomba guhabwa abarwaye COVID-19, abakekwaho kwandura n’ababonanye na bo ndetse n’abandi bantu bakeneye ubufasha muri rusange.
Ubufasha nsanamutima bugomba kujyana n’ishyirwaho ry’amatsinda yita ku buzima bwo mu mutwe ahuriweho n’inzego zinyuranye, uburyo busobanutse bwo guhana buri gihe amakuru mashya nyayo ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n’uburyo bwo kwita ku bayirwaye no gukoresha ibikoresho na porogaramu by’ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo abantu birinde kwegerana.
Inkingo zikora neza ni ngombwa kugira ngo hakumirwe ubwandu hagati y’inyamaswa zibana na virusi n’abantu banduye n’izindi nyamaswa cyangwa abantu bashobora kuba bafite virusi kandi usanga akenshi zunganira imiti irwanya virusi mu kwarwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi nshya.
Hari ibimaze gukorwa mu rwego rwo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S kugira ngo hakorwe abasirikare b’umubiri barwanya virusi mu gihe kirekire cyangwa kongera ubushobozi bw’umubiri bwo guhangana na SARS-CoV.
Inkingo zikoresha virusi zaciwe intege zasuzumiwe ku nyamaswa kuri SARS.
Ariko akamaro k’izi nkingo ku nyamaswa cyangwa abantu bazima bashaje n’abarembye cyane no mu kubarinda kwandura virusi zikomoka ku nyamaswa ntibishobora kumenyekana hatarakorwa ubushakashatsi bw’ubuvuzi.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n’uko hashize imyaka 17 SARS icitse noneho hakaba nta wundi muntu wongeye kuyirwara.
Ku rundi ruhande, abantu bake banduye MERS baracyakomeza kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati ndetse iyi virusi ikanakwirakwira mu tundi turere bitewe n’inyamaswa zikomeza kwanduza abantu mu turere turangwamo iyi virusi.
Hateguwe ingamba zo gukingira MERS hakoreshejwe virusi yambuwe ubushobozi, purasimide za ADN, vegiteri za virusi, uduce duto bikabije, uduce tumeze nka virusi n’uduce twa poroteyine twiyuburura kandi zimwe muri izi ngamba zusuzumiwe ku nyamaswa.
Gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2 rukora neza kandi rufite umutekano ku bantu badafite ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri bubarinda indwara ni ikintu gikenewe kandi cyihutirwa mu rwego rwo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ariko birakomeye gukemura iki kibazo kubera igihe kirekire (nk’amezi 18) gisabwa kugira ngo urukingo rukorwe n’imihindagurikire ya CoVs.
Nk’indwara nshya, COVID-19 yatangiye kugaragaza uburyo yavurwa mu bihumbi n’ibihumbi by’abayirwaye.
Akenshi abarwayi bashobora kugenda bakira nta ngaruka bibagizeho.
Ariko, kimwe no kuri SARS na MERS, COVID-19 na yo ifata abantu benshi kandi igahitana abantu benshi mu barwayi barembye.
Ni yo mpamvu gushyiraho uburyo bwo kuvura iyi ndwara ari ngombwa kugira ngo ibitaro n’amavuriro bishobora gukoresha neza serivisi zabyo cyangwa mu duce dufite ibikoresho bidahagije.
Hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw’ubuvuzi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa kujyana n’imivurirwe y’abarwaye COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe ​(Imbonerahamwe ya 33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni ikintu gikomeye cyane cyibanzweho mu gusuzuma imivurirwe ya SARS, akaba ari na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yafashe cyane cyane abafite hagati y’imyaka 30 na 65 muri bo 47,7% bakaba bari barengeje imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8 866 nk’uko byasobanuwe haruguru.
Abarwayi basabye gushyirwa mu byumba by’indembe akenshi bari bafite izindi ndwara n’ibindi bibazo kandi bari bakuze cyane kurusha abatarabisabye (mu kigero cy’imyaka 66 kuri 51), bivuze ko imyaka ari ikintu kigira uruhare mu mikirire y’abarwaye COVID-19.
Igitsina: Nk’uko byasobanuwe harugura abagabo ni bo banduye SARS-CoV-2 cyane (0,31/100 000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100 000).
Indwara zinyuranye n’ibibazo: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 basaba kujyanwa mu byumba by’indembe akenshi baba bafite ibibazo by’umutima wacitse ibisebe bikomeye kandi utera imbusane.
Imikorere y’umutima na yo yabaye impamvu nyamukuru y’urupfu rw’abarwaye SARS.
Byagaragajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 na yo ishobora gufata ku tunyangingo two ku gasabo k'indurwe dufite ACE2, bikaba byatera ibibazo by’umwijima mu barwaye COVID-19.
Birakwiye kuvuga ko imyaka n’indwara umuntu arwaye bifitanye isana ikomeye kandi ko bishobora kugiranaho ingaruka.
Imyanzuro ya raboratwari idasanzwe: Igipimo cya poroteyine zikorwa n’umwijima (CRP) mu maraso cyerekana ubukare bw’ububyimba cyangwa bw’ibisebe by’ingingo kandi cyagaragajwe ko gishobora kuba kimwe mu bishobora kugira uruhare mu mivurirwe y’indwara, mu buryo umuti wakirwa no mu gukira kw’umurwayi.
Isano iri hagati y’igipimo cya CRP n’ubukare n’imivurirwe ya COVID-19 na yo yaragaragajwe.
Ikindi kandi, igipimo cyo hejuru cy’imvubura zo mu bwoko bwa LDH, AST, ALT, na CK nazo zishobora gutuma umuntu amenya icyo kuvura indwara bizatanga.
Izi mvubura zigaragara cyane mu ngingo zinyuranye, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu mwijima, kandi zirekurwa iyo ibice by’umubiri byangiritse.
Ni yo mpamvu ari zo zisanzwe zerekana ibibazo by’umutima cyangwa umwijima.
Ibimenyetso by’ingenzi: Gucisha mu cyuma agatuza n’ibimenyetso bigaragara igihe gito bigomba kwitabwaho kimwe n’ibindi bibazo mu guteganya imivurirwe n’ibibazo bya COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa ry’imiti igabanya kubyimba: Nk’uko byavuzwe haruguru, imiti igabanya kubyimba ni imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri ikoreshwa cyane nk’imiti yunganira mu kuvura indwara zandura mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukare bw’ingaruka z’ubwirinzi bw’umubiri.
Kubera ko igipimo cyo hejuru cya korutikositeroyide umurwayi afata cyakoreshejwe cyane mu barwaye SARS barembye, abarwayi benshi babashije gukira barwaye indwara y’amagufa ijyana n’ubumuga bwa burundu n’ubuzima bubi.
Ni yo mpamvu, iyo zikenewe, abarwaye COVID-19 bagomba gufata igipimo cyo hasi cy’imiti igabanya kubyimba kandi mu gihe gito.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: Nk’uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy’icyorezo cya COVID-19 abarwayi benshi bagize umunaniro udasanzwe kubera kumara igihe kirekire mu kato no kwiheba bikabije ndetse no gupfusha abavandimwe ba hafi n’abo bari barwaranye.
Ni ngombwa guha aba barwayi ubujyanama bw’isanamitima n’ubufasha bw’igihe kirekire kugira ngo bibafashe gukira umunaniro ukabije no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Hakurikijwe ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n’aho ifite ibiyiranga bitandukanye n’ibya SARS.
Usibye kwibasira imyanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kujya neza mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu muhogo no mu mazuru no gutera ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa ntibitere mu minsi ya mbere y’ubwandu, nk’uko bigenda ku zindi virusi za CoVs zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ni yo mpamvu, abarwayi banduye mu minsi ya mbere cyangwa mu gihe bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare bashobora kugira umubare munini wa virusi bakora imirimo isanzwe, bityo bigatuma kurwanya iki cyorezo bikomera cyane.
Ariko hagaragajwe ko kwanduzanya SARS-CoV bibaho iyo abarwayi barembye, kubera ko abanduye benshi batanduye mu minsi ya mbere.
Ni yo mpamvu iki cyorezo cya COVID-19 gikaze kurushaho bikanaba bikomeye kukirwanya kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe harimo gufatwa ingamba nyinshi mu Bushinwa twavuga nka gahunda ya guma mu rugo muri Wuhan no mu mijyi iyikikije no gukomeza gushyira mu kato hafi abaturage bose mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo izi ngamba zashegeshe ubukungu bikabije n’izindi nzego z’imirimo mu gihugu, umubare w’abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanyuka, bikaba byerekana ko icyorezo kiri gusubira inyuma.
Ikigereranyo gishimishije cyane ni uko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, noneho igihe abantu bagenda basubira mu buzima busanzwe kikazamara hagati y’amezi 3 na 4.
Ariko hari impuguke zimwe na zimwe zidafite iki cyizere.
Paul Hunter na bagenzi be basanze COVID-19, isa n’iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini na bagenzi be bashyizeho uburyo bwo guteganya uko iki cyorezo kizarangira maze bavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gufata bibiri bya gatatu by’abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry’Abanyekanada batangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yatahuwe mu bizamini byafashwe mu gatuza no mu muhogo by’abarwayi bakize hashize ibyumweru 2 basezerewe mu bitaro, ibi bikaba byerekana ko iyi virusi nshya ishobora kuzajya igaruka nk’ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ariko hari ibimenyetso bitanga icyizere byagaragaye mu Bushinwa hashingiwe ku mubare w’abarwayi bashya ugenda ugabanyuka, bikaba byerekana ko ingamba zafashwe zishobora kuba zitanga umusaruro.
Abantu babanje kuvuga ko abantu miriyoni imwe bazarwara Ebola muri ibo ibihumbi magana atanu bagapfa.
Ariko kubera ingamba zikaze zo gushyira abantu mu kato, iyi ndwara yashoboye kuneshwa.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, birashoboka ko abantu bandura SARS-CoV-2 bagenda baba bake noneho igacika cyangwa se ikaba virusi itica cyane abantu bagendana.
Igereranya ry’icyorezo cya COVID-19 n’icya SARS na MERS turarisanga ahakurikira (Igishushanyo ​(Igishushanyo cya 55).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane binyuze mu gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura, kandi umuntu ashobora no kuyandura akoze ku bintu biriho iyi virusi.
Iyi virusi yanabonetse mu musarani, ibi bikaba bivuze ko hashobora kuba hariho uburyo bushya yanduriramo bwo kwikora ku munwa umuntu yakoze ku musarani.
Ubushakashatsi buheruka gukora ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by’abarwayi bashobora kuba baranduye bitewe n’ubwandu bwo mu bitaro, harimo abarwayi 17 bari barigeze kurwara izindi ndwara n’abaganga 40.
Bityo, hakenewe ubushishozi bwinshi mu rwego rwo kurinda abantu, cyane cyane abaganga, abasosiyari, abavandimwe b’abarwayi, abo bakorana, yewe n’abigendera bashobora guhura n’abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bushobora gukoreshwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni kwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two kwa muganga n’udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (icyiciro # 1860s) bifasha kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa two kwa muganga dufasha kwirinda ibitonyanga bivuye ku muntu ushobora kuba yaranduye bigenda mu mwuka cyangwa byarafashe ku bintu, noneho bikaba byajya ku bandi.
Ariko udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (icyiciro # 1860s) ni two twonyine dushobora kurinda umuntu kumira twa virusi tugenda mu mwuka tungana na 10 kugera kuri 80 nm, 5% by’utu tuvirusi akaba ari two dushobora kunyuramo; SARS-CoV-2 ingana na SARS-CoV mu bunini kandi zombi zijya kungana na 85 nm.
Kubera ko hari uduce dushobora kunyura no mu dupfukamunwa two kwa muganga dutanu tugerekeranye, abaganga babonana kenshi n’abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (icyiciro # 1860s) mu mwanya w’udupfukamunwa two kwa muganga.
Uretse kwambara udupfukamunwa, abaganga bagomba kwambara amakanzu yabugenewe kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya ibyago bwo guhura na virusi.
Virusi zinashobora gufata umuntu zinyuze mu maso.
Kuri 22 Mutarama 2020, hari umuganga wanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ko mu bwoko bwa N95; bivuze ko virusi yaba yarageze mu mubiri we inyuze mu maso.
Bityo, abaganga bagomba no kwambara ibibarinda mu maso cyangwa indorerwamo zabugenewe zibonerana mu gihe bari kwita ku barwayi.
Ku bantu muri rusange batuye mu turere twibasiwe cyangwa dushobora kwibasirwa na virusi, ni ngombwa rwose ko buri wese yajya akaraba intoki kenshi akoresheje isabune irimo imiti, akagerageza kwishyira mu kato aguma mu rugo kandi akirinda guhura n’abantu bashobora kuba baranduye.
Metero imwe n’igice ni yo ntera abantu bakwiye gusiga hagati yabo n’umurwayi.
Ibi bikorwa ni uburyo bufite akamaro mu kugabanya ibyago bwo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yaje mu bantu nka virusi nshya, kuba ifite ibintu byinshi ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV nk’uko byatangajwe kuri 7 Mutarama 2020 bigomba kuba byaratumye Ubushinwa bwikengera bikomeye bitewe n’uko bwari bucyibuka icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003.
Nyamara, kuri 19 Mutarama 2020 ni bwo umuyobozi w’Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara muri Wuhan yahumurije abaturage ababwira ko iyo virusi nshya itandura cyane kandi ko abantu batayanduzanya cyane bityo kurwanya no kurandura iyi ndwara bikaba atari ikibazo.
Ubu butumwa bwagabanyije cyane amakenga y’abaturage, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyarimo cyitegura iserukiramuco rya ‘Spring Festival’, nuko amahirwe yo gukumira iyi ndwara muri Wuhan ayoyoka gutyo.
Ibigo bishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa bishobora kwigira kuri iri somo rikomeye maze bikazakora impinduka zikomeye ubutaha.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba (1) gushishoza cyane mu gutanga amatangazo agenewe abaturage kubera ko abaturage bazirikana buri jambo noneho bakaba bahindura imyifatire n’ibyemezo byabo; (2) kurushaho gukurikira amakuru adasanzwe atangwa n’ibitaro no gufata ibyemezo bikwiye aho gutegereza raporo abaganga cyangwa abayobozi batanga mu buryo bwemewe; (3) gufata ingamba nyinshi zigamije gukumira icyorezo kibayeho cyose kigitangira aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; no (4) gutegura kenshi amahugurwa agenewe ibyiciro byihariye mu rwego rwo gufasha abaturage kurushaho kumenya ibijyanye n’indwara z’ibyorezo ndetse no kugerageza no kunoza ingamba zo guhangana na byo mu bihe bitandukanye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera y’Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose igihe twandikaga iyi raporo.
Kubera ko iyi virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV n’ibimenyetso na byo bikaba bisa hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu bagira ngo ni SARS igarutse.
Ariko hari ibintu bigaragara bitandukanya COVID-19 na SARS, bifite akamaro mu gukumira iki cyorezo no mu kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 ifata cyane abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko kandi ikabasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi n’ubukare n’igipimo cy’abapfa na byo biri hejuru mu bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko.
SARS ihitana abantu benshi kurusha COVID-19 (10,91% kuri 1,44%).
Abarwaye COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi n’igihe nta bimenyetso bibagaragaraho naho abarwaye SARS usanga akenshi banduza abandi igihe barembye, ibi bikaba bituma gukumira ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bikomera cyane kurusha SARS.
Ibi ni bimwe mu bigaragaza impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira vuba cyane n’ahantu hanini kurusha SARS-CoV.
Ikizamini cya RNA cyemewe kuri SARS-CoV-2 gishobora kutagaragaza ubwandu mu barwaye COVID-19 bamwe na bamwe.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera gusangwamo virusi.
Ibi byose byongera cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Hatirengagijwe iyi ntambwe ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bumaze gutera, ibibazo byinshi by’ingenzi bikurikira biracyakeye gusubizwa:
SARS-CoV-2 yaturutse he?
Nubwo hari imiterere imwe ku kigero cya 96% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na virusi ebyiri za CoVs zisa nka SARS zikomoka ku ducurama, ntidushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 ikomoka ku ducurama.
Ni iyihe nyamaswa yanduye bwa mbere virusi iyivanye ku nyamaswa virusi yakomotseho, tuvuge uducurama, maze ikayanduza abantu?
Mu gihe tutazi ibisubizo by’ikibazo cya 1 n’icya 2, ntidushobora guhagarika neza ikwirakwira rya virusi, n’icyorezo gishobora kugaruka igihe cyose.
Nubwo ibizamini ku miterere ya morekire no ku ngingo z’umubiri byerekanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata kuri ACE2, ni gute iyi virusi yinjira uturemangingo two mu mwuka maze igatera impinduka z’indwara zikurikiraho?
Iyi virusi yaba inafata ku turemangingo dukora ACE2 mu zindi ngingo z’umubiri?
Tutarabona ibisubizo bisobanutse by’ibi bibazo, ntidushobora gusuzuma iyi virusi vuba kandi neza no kuyivura bikwiye.
Iki cyorezo kizamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute imiterere y’iyi virusi igenda ihindagurika igihe ikwirakwira mu bantu?
Ese izaba icyorezo cyo ku isi hose, azacika nka SARS cyangwa izajya igenda igaruka nk’ibicurane?
Gushaka ibisubizo by’ibi bibazo n’ibindi bibazo byinshi ni ngombwa ariko bishobora kumara igihe.
Ariko, icyo byasaba cyose, nta yandi mahitamo dufite uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba bishoboka maze abantu bagasubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Inyamaswa zanduje abantu koronavirusi
Guhindagurika no kumenyera byatumye koronavirusi (CoVs) n’abantu cyangwa inyamaswa irimo bigenda bihinduka, mu myaka ibihumbi n’ibihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, CoVs (HCoVs) ebyiri zifata abantu zari zizwiho gutera indwara yoroheje, nk’ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ibyorezo by’ibicurane bikaze cyane (SARS) n’ibicurane byo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) byaje guhindura ibintu byerekana uko indwara ya HCoV ishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye no gushyira ubuzima mu kaga.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 byatumye CoVs zongera kuvugwaho cyane mu itangazamakuru iranadutangaza kubera uburyo yandura cyane ariko ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara ari buke ugereranyije na mugenzi wayo SARS-CoV.
Indwara ya HCoV ni indwara ikomoka ku nyamaswa bityo kumenya inyamaswa HCoVs yakomotseho byadufasha natwe.
HCoVs nyinshi zakomotse ku ducurama zikaba nta ndwara zidutera.
Inyamaswa zandujwe mbere zimwe muri za HCoVs na zo ntizizwi.
Kumenya inyamaswa zibana na zo bifite ingaruka zitaziguye mu kwirinda indwara zifata abantu.
Gukora ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire y’inyamaswa zibana na CoV na byo bishobora kugira akamaro mu kumenya uburyo CoV zitera abantu indwara.
Muri iri suzuma, turatanga incamake y’ubumenyi buhari ku bijyanye na HCoVs zirindwi, twibanda ku mateka y’uko zavumbuwe n’inyamaswa zakomotseho n’uburyo zikwirakwira hagati y’ubwoko bunyuranye.
Icy’ingenzi ni uko tugereranya HCoVs zitandukanye twibanda ku buryo virusi ihindagurika n’uko jenome yiyuburura.
Icyorezo cya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kiriho muri iki gihe kirasuzumwa muri uru rwego.
Ikindi kandi, ibyangombwa bisabwa kugira ngo virusi ibashe guhererekanwa n’ingaruka n’imihindagurikire ya virusi igira ku bukare bw’indwara na byo biragaragazwa.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ziri mu muryango wa ‘Coronaviridae’, ugizwe n’itsinda rya virusi za RNA zifite utwugara kandi zakirwa neza.
Izi virusi zibamo jenome nini zifite kilobaze 26 kugera kuri 32 muri virusi za RNA ziswe “CoVs” kubera ko muri mikorosikope ya elegitoronike ziba zimeze nk’ikamba.
Ku bijyanye n’imiterere, CoVs zifite jenome zidaciyemo ibice zihuje imiterere.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya jenome biba birimo utwugara tubiri tunini tugerekeranye turebeka nta kibazo (ORF1a na ORF1b), tuvamo poroteyine za pp1a na pp1ab zigira imimaro inyuranye.
Poroteyine zigira imimaro inyuranye na zo ziranonosorwa zikavamo poroteyine 16 zidateye kimwe hose, zitwa nsp1~16.
Igice gisigaye cya jenome kibamo ORFs za poroteyine ziteye kimwe hose, harimo umutwe (S), akugara (E), ingenangingo (M) na nikerewoporoteyine (N).
Poroteyine ngaragira nyinshi zijyana n’imiryango na zo zikorwa n’imiryango itandukanye ya CoVs.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro ry’imiterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zigabanyijemo ubwoko bune (alufa-CoV, beta-CoV, gama-CoV na delita-CoV), ubwoko bwa beta-CoV akaba ari bwo bubamo HCoVs nyinshi ndetse bukaba bugabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso ndangankomoko byerekanye ko uducurama n’ingugunnyi ari zo zikomokaho alufa-CoVs na beta-CoVs nyinshi, naho inyoni akaba ari zo zibana cyane na gama-CoVs na delita-CoVs.
Mu myaka ibihumbi n’ibihumbi, CoVs zakunze kwibasira ubwoko bunyuranye ndetse zimwe muri zo zagaragaye ari virusi zikomeye zishobora gutera abantu indwara.
Kugeza ubu, CoVs (HCoVs) zifata abantu zirindwi ni zo zizwi.
Muri zo dusangamo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 zibarirwa muri alufa-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoVs eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, koronavirusi itera ibicurane bikaze cyane (SARS-CoV), koronavirusi itera ibicurane byo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk’ibicurane bisanzwe cyangwa impiswi.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 imenyekanye vuba ni virusi zitera indwara cyane, zigatera indwara ikaze yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza mu barwayi benshi bagira ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka (ARDS) n’ibibazo byo hanze y’ibihaha.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwakomotse kuri HCoV-229E, B814, bwabonetse mu matembabuzi yo mu mazuru y’abarwayi barwaye ibicurane bisanzwe hagati mu 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, habonetse ubumenye bwinshi buvuye mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, zombi zikaba zitera ibimenyetso byikiza.
Ni byo koko, abantu benshi bari baremeye ko indwara iterwa na HCoVs ubusanzwe ntacyo itwara kugeza habayeho icyorezo cya SARS.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo bikaze cyane byabayeho mu mateka ya vuba, gifata abantu 8 000 abapfuye bagera nko ku 10%.
Nyuma y’imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy’ibicurane byo mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) cyavuyemo icyorezo gikunda kwibasira Umwigimbakirwa w’Abarabu rimwe na rimwe kikagera no mu bindi bice by’isi.
HCoV 2019 nshya (2019-nCoV), yaje guhindurirwa izina ikitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo yateye icyorezo cya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) kiriho muri iki gihe, kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020 kikaba cyari kimaze guhitana abantu 3 120 no gufata abarenga 91 000.
Hashize igihe abantu baburirwa n’isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo gitaha cya SARS-CoV-2.
HCoVs zirindwi zose zikomoka ku ducurama, imbeba cyangwa amatungo yo mu rugo.
Ibimenyetso binyuranye bihamya ko HCoVs zikomoka ku ducurama, izi virusi zikaba zikunda kubana na two nta ndwara zitera ariko bikerekana ko zifite jene zinyuranye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye ibibazo bikomeye mu rwego rw’ubuvuzi, ubumenyi, imibereho n’imyifatire mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gushaka kumenya inyamaswa HCoVs zikomokaho bitanga uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere, impamvu n’inzitizi byo gusimbuka ubwoko.
Ibi bishobora no gufasha cyangwa koroshya ibikorwa byo gushaka inyamaswa ibana na SARS-CoV-2, iyayanduye bwa mbere n’iyatumye ikwirakwira cyane, bikaba byagira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ikwirakwira ryayo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iri suzuma, turatanga incamake ku nyamaswa HCoVs zakomotseho, uburyo zikwirakwira hagati y’ubwoko bunyuranye n’uburyo zitera indwara.
By’umwihariko, turerekana tunasuzume imvugo imenyerewe ko virusi zibyara HCoVs ubusanzwe zidatera indwara inyamaswa zibana na zo ariko zigatera indwara umuntu cyangwa inyamaswa nshya zifashe nyuma yo gukwirakwira mu bwoko bunyuranye.
Turanasuzuma uko HCoV zigenda zihindagurika aho usanga gukwirakwira cyane akenshi bijyana no kugabanyuka kw’ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara.
Muri uru rwego turanasuzuma amaherezo y’icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiriho muri iki gihe.
CoVs zifata inyamaswa zizwi kuva mu mpeza za 1930.
Mbere yo kubona bwa mbere ubwoko bwakomotse kuri HCoV-229E, B814, mu matembabuzi yo mu mazuru y’abarwayi bari bararwaye ibicurane bisanzwe, hagaragaye CoVs zinyuranye zivanwe mu nyamaswa zanduye zinyuranye, twavuga nka dendo, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n’imbwa.
Mu myaka icumi ishize, habonetse HCoVs zirindwi.
Incamake y’amateka y’uko HCoVs zagiye zivumburwa (Imbonerahamwe ​1) yatanga amakuru n’uburyo abantu babyifatamo.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwakomotse kuri HCoV-229E bwabonetse mu myanya y’ubuhumekero y’abarwayi barwaye mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu muhogo no mu mazuru mu 1966, noneho nyuma y’aho buza kumenyera gukurira mu turemangingo tw’ibihaha twa WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by’ibicurane bisanzwe, twavuga nk’umutwe, kwitsamura, kumererwa nabi no kubabara mu muhogo, hamwe n’umuriro n’inkorora byabonetse mu 10~20% by’abarwayi.
Nyuma y’aho muri 1967, HCoV-OC43 yabonetse mu rugingo rw’umubiri iza no kugaragara mu bwonko bw’imbeba zonsa.
Ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga by’indwara ya HCoV-OC43 usanga bisa n’ibiterwa na HCoV-229E, bikaba bidashobora gutandukanywa n’indwara iterwa n’izindi virusi zibasira imyanya y’ubuhumekero nka virusi zitera ibicurane by’ibiguruka na virusi zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 zombi ziboneka ku isi hose, kandi zikunda gukwirakwira cyane mu rugaryi hari ibihe bihehereye.
Muri rusange, igihe bifata kugira ngo izi virusi zombi zigaragaze ibimenyetso ni munsi y’icyumweru, gikurikirwa n’uburwayi bumara nk’ibyumweru 2.
Nk’uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu babishaka, abantu batarwaye banduye HCoV-229E barwaye ibicurane bisanzwe bidakaze.
Abarwayi bake bari bafite ibibazo by’ubudahangarwa by’umubiri ni bo barwaye indwara ikaze yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza.
SARS, inazwi nk’“umusonga udasanzwe”, ni yo yabaye icyorezo cya mbere gitewe na HCoV cyakozweho ubushakashatsi bwimbitse mu mateka ya muntu ikaba yaratewe na SARS-CoV, HCoV yavumbuwe bwa gatatu.
Uwarwaye SARS bwa mbere yagaragaye mu mpera za 2002 mu Ntara ya Guangdong yo mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyafashe abantu 8 096 bemejwe ko barwaye hapfuyemo 774, gikwira mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse abanduje abandi cyane bikabije, hagaragajwe ko buri murwayi yashoboraga kwanduza nk’abandi bantu babiri, igihe bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare kikaba hagati y’iminsi 4 na 7 noneho virusi igakara cyane ku munsi wa 10 w’uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV babanje kugira ububabare mu ngingo, umutwe, umuriro, kumererwa nabi no gutitira, byakurikiwe no guhumeka bigoranye, inkorora n’ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka nk’ibimenyetso byagaragaye nyuma.
Igabanuka ry’ingirabuzima fatizo, ibizamini by’umwijima udakora neza n’ubwiyongere bwa kereyatine kinaze ni byo bibazo SARS igaragaza muri raboratwari.
Kwangirika bikomeye kw’umuyoboro w’umwuka (DAD), ikwirakwira ry’uturemangingo twa epiteriyumu n’ubwiyongere bw’uturemangingo two kwirinda na byo bigaragara mu barwaye SARS.
Nka 20-30% by’abarwayi bakenera kuvurirwa mu byumba by’indembe no gushyirwa ku mashini zibafasha guhumeka.
Uretse imyanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza, ingingo z’umubiri zinyuranye nk’urwungano ngongozi, umwijima n’impyiko na zo zishobora gufatwa muri aba barwayi barembye, akenshi bikajyana n’ubwiyongere bwa sitokine, bishobora kuba byavamo urupfu cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ibibazo by’ubudahangarwa by’umubiri.
Iyi virusi yabonetse bwa mbere mu gace kakaswe ku bihaha by’umurwayi wagaragaweho virusi bwa mbere wari wagiye muri Hongukongo avuye Guangzhou.
Kuva icyo gihe, hakozwe ibintu byinshi mu rwego rw’ubushakashatsi kuri HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yabonetse mu mwana w’amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Yabanje kugaragara cyane mu bana bato, abantu bakuze no mu barwayi bafite ibibazo by’ubudahangarwa by’umubiri barwaye indwara zo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero.
Ubushye bwo mu mazuru, gutukura amaso, umuriro nkubabuka mu jisho na boronshiyorite ni byo bikunze guterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje iyi virusi mu kizamini cyo mu izuru cyafashwe ku mwana w’umuhungu w’amezi 8 urwaye umusonga mu Buholandi.
Nubwo yagaragaye mu Buholandi, mu by’ukuri iboneka ku isi hose.
Bivugwa ko HCoV-NL63 itera nka 4,7% by’indwara zo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero zikunze kuboneka, kandi igaragara cyane mu ntangiriro z’icyi, mu itumba no mu rugaryi.
HCoV-NL63 ijyana na rarenjite ituma umuntu afungana mu muhogo no mu mazuru.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse mu mugabo w’imyaka 71 wari uri mu bitaro arwaye umusonga na boronshiyorite muri Hongukongo.
Uretse umusonga na boronshiyorite umuntu arwara bitewe n’aho aba, hatangajwe ko HCoV-HKU1 ituma abarwayi barembejwe n’asima barushaho kuremba.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 zagaragaye ku isi hose, zigatera indwara z’ubuhumekero zoroheje.
Izi HCoVs zose uko ari enye zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba zabashije kumenyera kuba mu bantu kandi muri rusange usanga zidashobora guhinduka kugira ngo zibe zatera indwara zifite virusi zandura cyane, nubwo habayeho impanuka zitewe n’impamvu zitazwi nk’urugero rudasanzwe rwa virusi ikaze cyane yo mu bwoko bwa HCoV-NL63, iherutse kuvugwaho ko itera indwara ikaze yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza mu Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, iyo izi HCoVs zibonye ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira cyane no kuguma mu bantu, zinagira ubukare buke cyangwa ubushobozi buke bwo gutera indwara.
MERS-CoV yabonetse bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by’umurwayi w’imyaka 60 warwaye umusonga ukaze n’impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abarwayi benshi bagaragajwe n’ibizamini byo muri raboratwari baturuka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, abaturutse ahandi rimwe na rimwe bakayanduza abandi babana bagaragajwe mu bihugu binyuranye by’i Burayi no muri Tuniziya.
Ikindi cyorezo cyoroheje cyabayeho muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 haboneka abarwayi bemejwe ko bacyanduye 186.
Ibimenyetso byo kwa muganga bya MERS bisa n’ibya SARS, bigaragazwa n’umusonga ugenda ukara.
Uretse SARS, abarwaye MERS banagize ibibazo by’impyiko bikomeye, bityo kugeza ubu bikaba ari umwihariko wa MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Hejuru ya 30% by’abarwayi bagira ibimenyetso by’indwara z’urwungano ngongozi, nk’impiswi no kuruka.
Kuva kuri 14 Gashyantare 2020, abarwayi bagaragajwe n’ibizamini byo muri raboratwari barenga 2500 hapfamo benshi bangana na 34,4%, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zihitana abantu benshi zizwi kugeza ubu.
Kuva hagati mu 2019 kugera mu mpera z’Ukuboza, abantu barwaye umusonga wari usanzwe umenyerewe ko ujyana no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 batahuwe muri Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo kiriho cy’indwara ikaze yo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero yo mu gatuza iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari amakuba abangamiye ubuzima rusange ahangayikishije isi rinita iyi ndwara COVID-19.
Kuri 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90 053 bari bemejwe ko banduye ku isi, ikigereranyo cy’abapfa kingana na 3,4%.
Muri uru rwego, igipimo cy’abapfuye muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa ni 4,2%, naho hanze y’iyi ntara ni 1,2%.
SARS-CoV-2 itera ibicurane bikaze nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, bijyana no kugira umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka bigoranye.
Abarwayi bamwe na bamwe barwaye n’impiswi.
Umusonga ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikaze cyane kandi uwufite ashobora kuremba vuba bikavamo kugira ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zimeze kimwe cyane bitewe n’ibintu byinshi zihuriyeho bigize imiterere ya nikerewotide ku kigero cya 82%, zigira amashami atandukanye ku giti ndangankomoko.
SARS-CoV-2 isa n’aho itera indwara gake ariko ikaba ikwirakwira cyane ugereranyije na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Hagaragaye abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 batagaragaza ibimenyetso bityo bakaba bashobora kuba bafite uruhare mu kuba ikwirakwira vuba ku isi.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 n’izindi HCoVs esheshatu byerekana ibintu zihuriyeho n’ibyo zitandukaniyeho bikwiye kwitabwaho.
Icya mbere, igihe bifata kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigaragare n’igihe indwara ya HCoV imara birahuye cyane.
Muri uru rwego, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikira umujyo rusange w’izindi HCoVs esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukare bw’ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 buri hagati y’ubwa SARS-CoV n’ubwa HCoVs enye zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku rundi ruhande, indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza ibimenyetso usanga bikunze kugaragara cyane mu gihe cy’ubwandu bwa HCoVs zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba, twavuga nko kugira ibimenyetso bitihariye, byoroheje cyangwa se no kutabigira.
Na none, umubare muto cyane w’abantu baremba barwaye COVID-19 na wo ushobora kuboneka igihe cy’indwara ya SARS-CoV, nubwo igipimo kiri hasi ho gato.
Icya gatatu, ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-CoV-2 na ryo ryerekana imisusire ikwiye kwitabwaho iranga HCoVs zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba na SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwa, usanga uburyo SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira usanga nibura buri hejuru kimwe n’ubwa HCoVs zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba.
Ku rundi ruhande, haracyakenewe kugenzurwa niba uburyo SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira bugabanyuka nyuma yo kwinjira mu bantu nk’uko bigenda kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Icya nyuma, kimwe no ku zindi HCoVs, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gutahurwa mu bizamini by’umusarane.
Ubushakashatsi butaha bukwiye kugaragaza niba ikwirakwizwa rya SARS-CoV-2 mu musarane no mu matembabuzi yo mu kanwa rigira uruhare rukomeye nk’uko bigenda kuri SARS-CoV nibura ahantu hamwe na hamwe.
Na none ni ngombwa kureba by’umwihariko niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bihe bitandukanye nk’uko bigenda kuri HCoVs zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba.
Nyamara, ibiranga SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo ikwirakwira, ubushobozi bwo gutera indwara no gukwirakwira birambye nyuma yo kujya mu bantu bizagira uruhare mu iherezo ry’icyorezo gikomeje cya COVID-19.
HCoVs zifata ubwoko bitewe n’aho buba zose uko ari enye zigira ibimenyetso byoroheje zabashije kumenyera abantu neza.
Ku rundi ruhande, byanashoboka ko mu by’ukuri ari n’abantu bashoboye kumenyera izi HCoVs enye.
Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba byararokotse ibyorezo bya HCoV byabayeho kera.
HCoVs zitera abantu indwara zikaze n’abantu barwara indwara zikaze ziterwa na HCoV barapfuye.
Kugira ngo bibeho, koronavirusi zifata umuntu (HCoV) zivamo utundi duce duhagije mu gutuma zibona uko zihinduka zikangiza poroteyine y’umubiri irwanya virusi iyibuza kwiyongera.
Bityo, uko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kimara igihe kikananduza abantu benshi, hari ibyago byinshi ko kizamenyera neza umubiri w’umuntu.
Nikimenyera neza, kwandura mu bantu biziyongera kubihagarika hakoreshejwe akato cyangwa izindi ngamba bizagorana.
Mu myaka myinshi, ubwoko bune bwa virusi za CoV zandurira hanze y’ibitaro zigenda mu bantu, zigatera inkorora abantu basanzwe bafite ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri.
Izo virusi ntizikenera kuba ziri mu nyamaswa.
Ku rundi ruhande, virusi za SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zitera indwara cyane ntizigeze zimenyera umubiri w’umuntu neza, bituma kwandura mu bantu bitamara igihe kirekire.
Zikenera kuguma kwiyongerera mu nyamaswa zibamo virusi zinategereje uko zagera ku bantu badafite ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri bukomeye, zinyuze mu nyamaswa imwe cyangwa nyinshi zikuriramo n’izo zororokeramo cyane.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite imiterere imeze nk’iya SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV na virusi ya HCoV enye zandurira hanze y’ibitaro.
Irandura cyane kimwe nka virusi za HCoV zandurira hanze y’ibitaro, byibuze kugeza ubu.
Ariko, itera indwara kurusha virusi za HCoV zandurira hanze y’ibitaro ntinanatere indwara cyane nka SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Haracyategerejwe kureba niba izamenyera neza abantu no kugenda mu bantu nta nyamaswa ivuyemo.
Mbere yo kuvuga ku nyamaswa zakomotseho virusi ya HCoV, byaba byiza tuganiriye ku bisobanuro n’ibiranga inyamaswa virusi za HCoV zihindukiramo, zibana na zo mu buryo karemano, zigira indiri, zikuriramo n’izo zororokeramo cyane.
Inyamaswa ni yo ituma virusi ya HCoV ikura iyo ifitanye isano ya hafi n’iyo ikomokaho bisangiye byinshi ku rwego rw’imiterere y’isanomuzi.
Ubusanzwe virusi y’inyamaswa ikomokaho iba yaramenyereye kandi ntitere indwara iyi nyamaswa irimo.
Bityo inyamaswa yagizwe indiri ikomeza kuba indiri ya virusi ya HCoV kandi bikamara igihe kirekire.
Kuri izo mpamvu zombi, inyamaswa zirimo virusi ziba zaranduye mu buryo karemo zirimo virusi ya HCoV cyangwa virusi iyibyara.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo HCoV ije ari nshya mu nyamaswa ikuriramo mbere gato cyangwa hafi yo kuba yakwanduza abantu, ntimenyera neza aho igiye kandi akenshi itera indwara.
Iyo nyamaswa ikuriramo ishobora kuba ari yo yakwanduza abantu ikanaba inyamaswa yororoheramo cyane ituma virusi yiyongera vuba maze ikayanduza abantu mu kongera igipimo cy’ubwandu bwa muntu.
Virusi ya HCoV ishobora kutagira uwo yanduza igihe itabashije guhinduka iri mu nyamaswa ikuriramo.
Ku rundi ruhande, HCoVs ishobora kumenyera inyamaswa ikuriramo maze ikayigumamo igihe kirekire.
Iyo bimeze bityo, inyamaswa ikuriramo ihinduka inyamaswa yagizwe indiri mu buryo karemano.
Amakuru y’ibyorezo yagaragaje ko uwagaragaweho bwa mbere na virusi ya SARS yayanduriye mu mukino wo guhiga inyamaswa.
Ibipimo by’amaraso byakurikiyeho byagaragaje ko abacuruzi b’inyamaswa bari bihariye ubudahangarwa bw’umubiri burwanya SARS-CoV IgG ugereranyije n’abaturage basanzwe.
Impimbi n’imbwa yo mu bwoko bw’impimbi mu masoko abagirwamo inyamaswa bwa mbere zagaragaye ko zifite virusi zimeze nka SARS-CoV isa cyane nka SARS-CoV.
Ibi byemejwe mu buryo butaziguye ni uko SARS yakomeje kuvugwa nyuma yo kwica ipimbi zose ziri mu masoko.
Ariko, byavuzwe ko impimbi zo mu mashyamba cyangwa mu nzuri zitigeze zihura n’inyamaswa zo mu masoko abagirwamo inyamaswa zapimwe bagasanga zidafite SARS-CoV, bivuze ko impimbi na zo zishobora kuba inyamaswa SARS-CoV ikuriramo ikanororokeramo cyane ariko idashobora kubana na zo mu buryo karemano.
By’umwihariko, mu gihe 80% by’inyamaswa zitandukanye mu masoko yo muri Guangzhou zifite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV, ntawahakana ko ubwoko bwinshi bw’inyamabere nto SARS-CoV ishobora gukuriramo no kororokeramo cyane.
Izo zose bigaragara ko zidashobora kwanduza SARS-CoV.
Ubushakashatsi bwakurikiyeho bukorerwa inyamaswa zirimo virusi itarakura ya SARS-CoV bwagaragaje ko virusi ya CoV isa cyane na CoV yo mu ducurama, yiswe SARS yo mu ducurama CoV HKU3 (SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3), iba mu ducurama two mu Bushinwa.
Utwo ducurama dufite abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV n’imiterere ya jenome ya SARSr-Rh-BatCoV HKU3.
Izi n’izindi CoV zo mu ducurama bisangiye 88-92% by’imiterere y’isanomuzi cya SARS-CoV.
Ubwo bushakashatsi bwashimangiye igitekerezo gishya ko uducurama turimo virusi itarakura dutera abantu indwara.
SARS nyinshi zimeze nka CoV (SL-CoVs) zagaragaye mu ducurama, ariko nta n’imwe uretse iyitwa WIV1 ifatwa nka virusi yatera indwara.
Umusemburo wa anjiyotensini ihindura anzime uba mu muntu (ACE2) izwiho kwakira SARS-CoV.
WIV1 yakuwe mu bipimo by’umusarani w’uducurama ikoresha ACE2 y’agacurama, impimbi n’abantu mu kwinjira mu mubiri.
Igitangaje ni uko serumu y’abarwayi bakira SARS yashoboye guca intege virusi ya WIV1.
Kugeza ubu, WIV1 igaragaza ko ikomoka cyane kuri SARS-CoV yo mu ducurama, bikaba bisangiye 95% mu gusa ku isanomuzi.
N’ubwo izo virusi ebyiri zifitanye isano ya hafi, muri rusange hatekerezwa ko WIV1 atari yo ibyara virusi ya SARS-CoV kandi uducurama si two ndiri virusi ya SARS-CoV ikuriramo.
Isesengura ry’imihindagurikire ya virusi rishyira MERS-CoV mu itsinda rimwe virusi za CoV-HKU4 na CoV-HKU5 zo mu ducurama.
CoV-HKU4 yo mu ducurama na MERS-CoV zakirwa na poroteyine ya DPP4 imwe, ikoreshwa na virusi mu kwinjira mu mubiri.
Poroteyine y’imiterere ya polimerase ya RNA yo mu MERS-CoV isa cyane na virusi ngenzi yayo ifata uducurama ya beta-CoV yabonetse mu Burayi n’Afurika.
Kugeza ubu, nta virusi nzima ya MERS-CoV wabona mu ducurama two mu ishyamba.
MERS-CoV n’indi virusi bisa cyane yo mu ducurama ya CoV-HKU25 bihuje gusa 87% ku isanomuzi.
Bityo, uducurama dushobora kuba atari two ndiri virusi ya MERS-CoV ikuriraho.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati bwagaragaje ko ingamiya zifitemo abasirikare baca intege by’umwihariko virusi ya MERS-CoV, kimwe nk’ingamiya zikomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati zo mu bihugu byinshi by’Afurika.
Virusi nzima ya MERS-CoV isa nka virusi igaragara mu bantu yakuwe mu bipimo byo mu mazuru by’ingamiya, bigaragaraza kurushaho ko ingamiya ari indiri nyayo ya virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Biranakwiye kuvuga muri rusange ari ibimenyetso byoroheje ariko bigaragaza ko virusi yakuze ikanava ku bwinshi byagaragaye mu ngamiya zakoreweho ubushakashatsi zikanduzwa virusi ya MERS-CoV.
By’umwihariko, ingamiya zanduye virusi zayirekuye bitanyuze gusa mu nzira z’ubuhumekero ahubwo binanyuze mu musarani, bikaba ari na yo nzira y’ibanze virusi zanduramo zivuye mu ducurama.
Ariko, hari ibibazo bikibazwa kuko abenshi bemejwe ko banduye virusi ya MERS batigeze bahura n’ingamiya mbere yo gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso, byakwitwa ko abantu banduje abandi cyangwa bitazwi aho banduriye bikaba bishoboka ko amoko y’inyamaswa atazwi afite virusi ya MERS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite 96,2% by’igice cy’isanomuzi na CoV RaTG13 yo mu gacurama yakuwe mu bwoko bw’uducurama.
Ku byerekeye virusi za SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, imiterere itandukanye hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni minini cyane ku buryo ntawavuga ko zikomoka hamwe.
Uducurama dushobora kuba atari two ndiri virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ikuriramo keretse mu minsi iri imbere hagaragaye isa na CoV ikurira mu ducurama.
Birashoboka ko inyamaswa zikuriramo SARS-CoV-2 ziba ari zo mu mashyamba zigurishwa zikabagirwa mu Isoko rya Huanan Seafood Wholesale, aho abenshi mu banduye bwa mbere COVID-19 baturutse, bikaba ari ikimenyetso kigaragaza ko bishoboka ko inyamaswa zanduje abantu.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi buherutse gukorwa bushingiye ku miterere ya metajenome, bwavuze ko itsinda ry’inyamabare nto ziri mu kaga zizwi nk’igisamujyonjyo na zo zishobora kuba zikomokaho virusi ya beta-CoV ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Izo jenome za CoV nshya z’igisamujyonjyo zifite 85-92% by’isanomuzi rya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, zifitanye isano ingana na RaTG13 bikaba bisa kuri 90% ku rwego rw’isanomuzi.
Ziri mu matsinda abiri mato bisa ya virusi zisa nka SARS-CoV-2 mu mihindagurikire ya virusi, imwe muri yo ifite poroteyine ituma ifata ku ngirabuzimafatizo (RBD) isa nk’iya SARS-CoV-2 kuri 97,4% by’ibiranga imiterere ya aside amino.
Ku buryo butandukanye cyane, RBD za SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ziratandukanye cyane, nubwo zisa ku rugero rwo hejuru mu byerekeye isano rya jenome.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku ndwara zifata igisamujyonjyo byanavuze ko hatahuwe uduce tw’isanomuzi twa virusi two mu bipimo byo mu bihaha, bikaba bifitanye isano risa na SARS-CoV-2.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwakoresheje uburyo butandukanye bwo guhuza no gutoranya hatangwa imwe mu miterere ya jenome igizwe na 86,3% bya jenome yose ya virusi.
Twitareka kuvuga ko bishoboka ko igisamujyonjyo ari kimwe mu nyamaswa zikuriramo virusi y a SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko, ubu nta bimenyetso byemeza ko virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ikomoka bitaziguye ku gisamujyonjyo kuko imiterere itandukanye hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoV ifata igisamujyonjyo.
Kandi, intera iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 ni ngufi y’iri hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoV ifata igisamujyonjyo.
Inzira y’ihinduka rya SARS-CoV-2 mu ducurama, ibisamujyonjyo n’izindi nyamaswa igomba gusobanurwa.
Mu gihe imiterere y'isano ikomeye yagaragaye muri RBD hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 n’igisamujyonjyo, SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoVs, SARS-CoV-2 na RaTG13 bisangiye imiterere y’isano rya jenome ikomeye.
Biravugwa cyane ko urugero rwo hejuru rwo gusa hagati ya RBD ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoV ifata igisamujyonjyo na SARS-CoV-2 iterwa n’ihinduka rigendera ku gutoranya.
Undi mushinga urifuza guhinduranya ingirangingofatizo hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoV ifata igisamujyonjyo na RaTG13 igaterwa mu moko ya gatatu y’inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba.
Ku byerekeye igitera ihinduka, guhinduranya ingirangingofatizo birakorwa cyane muri za beta-CoV.
Inteko iracyasesengura ku nyamaswa ikuriramo virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Usibye HCoV zitera indwara cyane, ikomoka rya HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-HKU1 ku nyamaswa na ryo ryakozweho ubushakashatsi.
Ibimenyetso by’imihindagurikire ya virusi byagaragaje ko HCoV-NL63 na HCoV-229E zishobora kuba zarakomotse kuri CoV yo mu gacurama, mu gihe virusi zibyara HCoV-OC43 na HCoV-HKU1 zasanzwe mu ngugunnyi.
Byavuzwe ko CoV yo mu gacurama yiswe ARCoV.2 (CoV yo mu misozi ya Appalachia) yatahuwe mu gacurama k’amabara atatu ko muri Amerika ya ruguru yagaragaje isano ya hafi na HCoV-NL63.
Ku rundi ruhande, HCoV-229E yari ifite isano ishingiye kuri jene n’indi CoV yo mu gacurama, yiswe Hipposideros/GhanaKwam/19/2008, yatahuwe muri Gana, mu gihe ubwoko bw’ingamiya bwaketsweho kuba bukuriramo iyo virusi.
Mu kubisobanura neza, ubumenyi buhari ku nyamaswa bizwi ko yazanye virusi ya HCoVs yavuzwe muri make mu gishushanyo cya​1 n’imbonerahamwe ya 2.
Isesengura ry’imihindagurikire ya virusi ryatanze ibimenyetso ko mu mateka habayeo kwanduzanya hagati y’amoko kwa HCoV.
Igihe HCoV-OC43 yavuye mu moko amwe akanduza abantu biturutse ku matungo yororerwa mu ngo ahagana mu 1890, hagaragaye icyorezo cy’indwara yo mu buhumekero.
Amateka yo kwanduzanya hagati y’amoko kwa virusi ya HCoV-229E ntagaragara neza.
alpha-CoV yo mu gacurama isa na HCoV-229E yaragaragaye.
Hagati yazo harimo alpha-CoV ifata arupaga.
Ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira ko kwandura kwa virusi iturutse mu ducurama igahita ijya mu bantu.
Icya mbere, abantu atari za arupaga, bahurira n’uducurama henshi mu buturo basangiye.
Ariko, abantu ni bo bakunda guhura cyane na za arupaga.
Icya kabiri, HCoV-229E ijyanye na alpha-CoV yo mugacurama ntizisa kandi ntizanduza uducurama, aho alpha-CoV yo muri arupaga yatewe n’icyorezo cyo mu buhumekero mu nyamaswa.
Hanyuma, alpha-CoV yo muri arupaga yasanzwe mu nyagasozi.
Bityo, ntawashidikanya ko za arupaga zandujwe HCoV-229E ijyanye na alpha-CoV n’abantu.
Muri make, uducurama ni two twanduza abantu virusi itera ibisazi, virusi itera ebola, virusi ya Nipah na virusi ya Hendra.
Bityo, ntibitangaje cyane kubona uducurama dushobora guhita twanduza abantu virusi ya HCoV-229E.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n’ubwo, aho alpha-CoVs ari itsinda rya jene rya HCoV-229E, za arupaga n’ingamiya zishobora kuba zakuriramo virusi zikananduza virusi abantu, bimeze neza nko kuri virusi ya MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ni urugero rwiza rwo kwanduzanya virusi hagati y’amoko uhereye ku ducurama ukagera ku ngamiya ukanahera ku ngamiya ukageza ku bantu.
Imihindagurikire y’inkomoko ya MERS-CoV yo mu ducurama izwi mu gihe yamenyekanye bwa mbere kandi byanashimangiwe n’ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi byakurikiyeho.
Biragaragara ko uducurama ari itsinda rikomeye rya virusi zo mu nyamaswa mu ihererekanya ry’uduce twa jene no kwanduzanya hagati y’inyamaswa.
Kuramba, gutura ahantu hamwe, kubana bya hafi n’ubushobozi bukomeye bwo kuguruka ni byo bintu bituma uducurama tuba inyamaswa zikomeye mu 'gukwirakwiza virusi'.
Ku rundi ruhande, hashize imyaka myinshi virusi ya MERS-CoV yinjiye mu ngamiya.
Yamenyereye neza izo ngamiya zaretse kuba inyamaswa ikuriramo zikaba inyamaswa zigirwa indiri ya virusi zibamo zitekanye no mu buryo karemano.
Virusi ya MERS-CoV itera indwara idakomeye kandi ikomeza kugenda ihinduka gahoro muri izo nyamaswa.
Kwandura ikagera mu bantu ni impanuka kandi abantu ntibanduza virusi ya MERS-CoV kuko ikwirakwira ryayo ridakomeye.
Ku bitandukanye n’uruhare rw’ingamiya mu kwanduza MERS-CoV, uruhare rw’ibisamujyonjyo niba ruhari, mu kwanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ruratandukanye.
By’umwihariko, beta-CoV yo mu bisamujyonjyo itera indwara cyane mu bisamujyonjyo.
Zishobora kuba zirimo virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ijyanye na beta-CoV ariko zitayanduza bisa nko ku mpimbi kuri SARS-CoV.
Birashoboka cyane ko inyamaswa zanduzanya SARS-CoV-2, inyamaswa na zo zikanduza abantu byakwemezwa cyangwa ntibyemezwe mu bushakashatsi bw’ahazaza.
Icya mbere, uducurama dushobora kuba ari ndiri ya virusi ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 ijya gusa na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bashobora gusangira ubuturo n’uducurama binyuze mu kutubaga no gucukura amakara.
Icya kabiri, ibisamujyonjyo bishobora kuba ari zimwe mu nyamaswa virusi zikuriramo zikanororokeramo cyane zifashwe vuba na virusi zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bandura virusi biturutse mu kubaga no kurya inyama z’inyamaswa z’ishyamba.
Birashoboka ko inyamabere nyinshi harimo n’amatungo yo mu rugo zikekwaho kuba zifite virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ubushakashatsi ku matungo yo mu rugo n’inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba bwasanze zifite abasirikare barwanya virusi.
Icya gatatu, ku byavuzwe ku guhinduranya ingirangingofatizo no kumenyera kwa SARS-CoV-2 bishobora kuba byarabayeho mu bwoko bwa gatatu bw’inyamaswa zahuye n’uducurama n’ingamiya.
Gushakisha inyamaswa itera SARS-CoV-2 birakomeje.
Usibye amoko atandukanye y’inyamaswa zikuriramo virusi, ibintu bitatu ku ruhande rwa virusi na byo ni ingenzi mu korohereza CoV kujya mu yandi moko y’inyamaswa.
Mbere na mbere, ni igipimo cyo guhinduka kinini cyane mu kwikoramo utundi duce twa RNA.
Zigereranyijwe n’izindi virusi za jene imwe ya RNA, guhinduka kwa CoV kuri mu “rugero” cyangwa “hejuru” n’impuzandengo yo guhindura jene ni ~10-4 ku mwaka kuri buri jene 2, bitewe n’icyiciro cy’imenyera rya CoV mu nyamaswa nshya yagiyemo.
CoV ifite anzime ihindura RNA, igasiba ibice byayo bituma ihinduka cyane igacika intege cyangwa ntibe yanabaho.
Igitangaje ni uko ku gice cy’isanomuzi, umuti wa Remdesivir uzwiho guhagarika kwikoramo utundi duce kwa CoV hifashishijwe anzime ibuza poroteyine ya polimerase ya RNA gukora.
Remdesivir ni umwe mu muti utanga icyizere ku kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 wasuzumwe n’abaganga.
Nyamara, guhinduka kwa CoV ni hafi miliyoni kurusha inyamaswa izo virusi zikuriramo.
Kandi, guhinduka akenshi biba biri hejuru iyo CoV zitamenyereye neza inyamaswa zikuriramo.
Mu kugereranya SARS-CoV ihinduka cyane, guhinduka kwa SARS-CoV-2 kuri hasi bigaragara, bikaba ari byo bituma imenyera cyane abantu.
Bivugwa ko yari yaramaze kumenyera indi nyamaswa hafi cyane y’abantu.
Usibye SARS-CoV-2, ibi binareba MERS-CoV, yamenyereye neza kuba mu ngamiya.
Bityo, ntibyashoboka ko guhinduka kwa jene byatuma inkingino n’imiti igabanya ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2 byacika intege vuba.
Icya kabiri, jenome nini ya RNA iri muri CoVs ikoresha ubundi buryo bwo guhindura imiterere muri jenome igahinduka ikanahinduranya ingirangingofatizo; bityo, ikongera amahirwe yo guhindukana n’inyamaswa ibamo, bikaba ari inyungu mu mikurire ya virusi nshya za CoV igihe bikwiye.
Ibi bishimangirwa n’imiterere ya RNA ivamo poroteyine n’imikorere yayo isobetse y’umusozo wa 3 wa jenome.
Icya gatatu, CoV irahinduka kandi kenshi ikavamo utundi duce twa RNA binyuze mu buryo bwo “guhindura jenome ikenewe”.
Mu nyamaswa ikurimo, guhinduka kwa jenome bibaho kenshi igihe RNA ya CoV iri kujya ku ngirangingofatizo.
RNA zisa cyane kandi zifite jenome zungirije zishobora guhindura ingirangingofatizo zigatanga CoV nshya.
Imihindagurikire karemano ya virusi yasanzwe muri HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-OC43, ndetse na CoV zifata inyamaswa nka SL-CoV na batCoV-HKU9 ziba mu ducurama.
Imibanire ya virusi n’inyamaswa ibamo mu byo kwanduzanya
Usibye virusi eshatu zavuzwe haruguru, imibanire ya virusi n’inyamaswa ikuriramo ni ikindi kintu gituma habaho kwanduzanya hagati y’ubwoko bunyuranye.
Bityo, guhinduka kwa SARS-CoV bifatwa nk’urugero rufatika, byanagaragaje guhitamo neza igice cy’umubiri virusi ijyamo mu kwanduzanya hagati y’inyamaswa.
Hashingiwe ku isesengura rigereranya hagati ya SARS-COV ifata abantu n’impimbi, hatekerezwa ko SARS-CoV imenyera vuba imibiri itandukanye ibamo, by’umwihariko ihinduka rya RBD rya poroteyine ya S.
Muri rusange, RBD yo muri poroteyine ya S ya virusi ya CoV ibana n’ingirangingofatizo iyakira kandi itoranywa bitewe n’uko irwanywa n’abasirikare b’umubiri yinjiyemo.
Muri SARS-CoV, RBD iri ku mwanya wa 318 kugeza ku wa 510 muri aside amino zo ku gice cya S1, bigatuma ifata kuri ACE2 y’umuntu ndetse akaba ari na ho virusi ishingira yinjira mu mubiri.
RBD ya SARS-CoV ishobora kumenya ACE2 zakira virusi z’inyamaswa zitandukanye, harimo agacurama, impimbi, imbeba, ubwoko bw’impimbi, bituma inyamaswa zanduzanya virusi.
Muri make, ibisigazwa bya aside amino 6 gusa ni byo byasuzumwe hasangwa bitandukanye n’iby’abantu n’impimbi bifite virusi muri RBD kandi 4 muri byo bifite igice kibihuza na ACE2 yakira virusi.
SARS-CoV yo mu mpimbi ifite imihindukire ya K479N na S487T muri RBD yayo, bishobora kongera isano ry’imibanire na poroteyine ya S hamwe na ACE2 y’umuntu yakira virusi.
Mu yandi magambo, guhindura izo aside amino ebyiri bishobora kuba ari ingenzi mu gutuma virusi imenyera umubiri w’umuntu.
Birashishikaje kumenya ko SARS-CoV-2 yakirwa n’ingirangingofatizo imwe nk’iyakira SARS-CoV.
Kuri 30% by’itandukaniro hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV mu gice cya S1 cya poroteyine ya S bigaragaza isano iyo poroteyine ya S ifitanye na ACE2 yo mu bantu ishobora kuba yarahinduwe.
Mu by’ukuri, ubushakashatsi kuri cryo-EM bugaragaza ubwikube 10 - 20 bw’isano rikomeye ryo kwihuza kwa ACE2 yo mu bantu na poroteyine ya S yo muri SARS-CoV.
Biranashishikaje kwemeza niba hari indi ngirangingofatizo yakira virusi yifashishwa mu kwanduza SARS-CoV-2.
Igitangaje ni uko HCoV-NL63 na yo yihuza na ACE2 ariko ku gice gitandukanye cya poroteyine ya S.
Hari izindi ngirangingo zakira HCoV, nka aminopepitidaze N ya HCoV-229E, na aside siyalike ifite asetili 9-O ya HCoV-OC43.
Bishobora gusobanura ukuntu virusi za CoV zimenyera umubiri w’umuntu azandujwe n’inyamaswa zakuriyemo.
Usibye ingirangingofatizo zakira virusi, kuba inyamaswa zanduzanya virusi ya HCoV binagengwa n’aho zikurira na poroteyine irwanya virusi.
Itandukaniro ry’izo poroteyine z’aho virusi zikurira hagati y’abantu n’inyamaswa zagizwe indiri karemana ya virusi za HCoV nk’uducurama, ingamiya n’ingugunnyi bishobora gukumira kwanduzanya virusi hagati y’ubwoko bunyuranye.
HCoV zihinduramo ingirangingo z’aho ziri maze zikangiza poroteyine irwanya virusi kugira ngo zibashe kwanduza izindi nyamaswa.
Bityo, ibice bya molekire muri iyi mibanire ikomeye ya virusi n’inyamaswa ikuriramo bikwiye gukomeza kugaragazwa no gusobanurwa.
Isuzuma rya jenome ndakemwa ry’aho virusi ikurira na poroteyine irwanya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rigezweho rya CRISPR bishobora gutanga umusaruro.
Kwigaragaza kwa virusi nshya ya HCoV: Inkomoko yayo
Amoko menshi ya CoV yo mu ducurama atanga amahirwe akomeye yo kwigaragaza kwa virusi nshya ya HCoV.
Bityo, CoV yo mu ducurama ni yo ivamo jene za HCoV.
Kandi guhinduka vuba no guhinduranya jene bituma HCoV ihindagurika bikaba ari intambwe ebyiri zikomeye muri iki gikorwa.
Urugero: Kubona cyangwa gutakaza jene zikora poroteyine bifite ubushobozi bwo guhindura cyane agace ka virusi.
Muri poroteyine ngereka za SARS-CoV, bitekerezwa ko ORF8 ari ingenzi mu kumenyera umubiri w’umuntu, naho virusi zo mu ducurama zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV zashyizwe ukwazo bigaragara ko zikora poroteyine itandukanye ya ORF8.
Isanomuzi ya 29 isiba SARS-CoV yagaragaye muri jene mu ntangiriro z’icyorezo cyibasiye abantu.
Iri siba rigabanya ORF8 mo ORF8a na ORF8b kandi bitekerezwa ko ishobora kumenyera ihinduka rituma ihinduranya inyamaswa.
Kandi SARS-CoV izwiho guhindura ingirangingofatizo z’amoko ya virusi za alpha na gamma-CoV, aho umubare munini w’ingirangingofatizo zahinduwe zasazwe muri poroteyine ya polimerase ya RNA.
Ahahinduwe ingirangingofatizo hanagaragaye muri nsp9, inyinshi muri nsp10, n’ibice bya nsp14.
Mu buryo bumwe binagaragara ko icyorezo cya MERS-CoV cyahinduye ingirangingofatizo hagati y’amoko abiri ya virusi atandukanye bikaba byarabaye mu ngamiya zo muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Usibye SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ibikorwa byo guhindura ingirangingofatizo byanagaragaye mu zindi HCoV, aho HCoV ihindura ingirangingofatizo za CoV z’indi nyamaswa muri jene zihariye zayo.
Birakwiye kumenya ko guhitamo bitari karemano byagira uruhare mu mpinduka zitagamijwe muri jenome za virusi, bika byatuma virusi zisohoka muri icyo gice cyatoranyijwe, nk’urugero abasirikare b’umubiri w’inyamaswa virusi ibamo.
Urugero rw’iyo mikorere ni kutagira jene isanzwe ya ORF4 muri HCoV-229E bigatuma isanomuzi nyabubiri isibwa.
Mu gihe ORF4 ikomeye yasanzwe muri virusi zo mu gacurama na lama zifitanye isano na HCoV-229E, alpha-CoV yo muri arupaga igaragaza kwinjirwamo n’isanomuzi imwe, bituma ihinduka.
Icya nyuma, imihindagurikire ya virusi nshya za HCoV inaterwa n’ibibazo byo kutaramba kw’inyamaswa zigira indiri.
Kutagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa byatahuwe ubwo uducurama twanduzwagwa CoV, bikagaraza kumenyerana hagati ya CoV n’uducurama.
Biragaragara ko uducurama tumenyerana neza na CoV mu rwego rw’imiterere y’umubiri.
Urugero: Kudakora neza kwa molekire zirwanya indwara mu ducurama bigabanya neza indwara ziterwa na virusi ya CoV.
Kandi ingirangingofatizo zica virusi mu buryo karemano mu ducurama zaretse gukora bitewe no kongeramo ingirangingofatizo zakira virusi za NKG2/CD94 no kutagaragara cyane kwa molekire igenga imikoranire ya tisi yo mu bwoko bwa I.
Kandi, urugero rwo hejuru rw’ibinyabutabire birimo ogisijeni (ROS) bituruka ku bikorwa byinshi by’umubiri w’uducurama bishobora guhagarika CoV ntiyikoremo utundi duce maze bikagira ingaruka mu gukosora ibyakozwe na anzime ihindura jene, bityo guhitamo jene za virusi bigatera indwara cyane igihe zigiye mu nyamaswa nshya.
Izindi jene zitera indwara za CoV nazo zirahinduka, hakaboneka poroteyine nshya cyangwa ibice byayo bituma inyamaswa imenyera iyo virusi.
Bityo, si amahirwe kuba virusi eshatu nshya za HCoV zaragaragaye mu myaka makumyabiri ishize.
CoV ntizitera indwara cyangwa ibimenyetso byoroheje inyamaswa zagize indiri nk’uducurama n’ingamiya.
Zihinduka cyane zitarwanyijwe bikomeye n’abasirikare b’umubiri zikuriramo.
Aha ni ho hari ibanga ry’impamvu inyamaswa zirimo iyo virusi zitagaragaza ibimenyetso n’ibituma abantu barwara cyane.
Ibimenyetso bikomeye ahanini biterwa n’ikora cyane ry’abasirikare b’umubiri no kurekura sitokine nyinshi, uko abasirikare barushaho kurwanya indwara ni na ko ibihaha birushaho kwangirika.
Bikaba bitandukanye ku nyamaswa zitagaragaza ibimenyetso, aho abasirikare b’umubiri bikura kuri virusi ya CoV iri guhinduka.
Kwitandukanya kw’abasirikare b’umubiri bishobora kugira akamaro mu kuvura virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Poroteyine irwanya virusi zirakomeye mu ducurama.
Bityo, gutanga poroteyine irwanya virusi yo mu bwoko bwa I byibuze umuntu acyandura SARS-CoV-2 byagira akamaro.
Na poroteyine ya NLRP3 irwanya virusi ntikora mu ducurama.
Hakurikijwe ibi bitekerezo, kubuza poroteyine ya NLRP3 ifite MCC950 gukora byagira umumaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Kugaragara kwa SARS-CoV-2 gukurikira uko virusi SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zaje.
Mu gihe byagaragaye ko beta-CoV yo mu gacurama bisangiye isanomuzi rya 95% na SARS-CoV, ni na ko isangiye isanomuzi rya 96% na SARS-CoV-2.
Mu gihe byasanzwe ko impimbi n’izindi nyamaswa zo mu masoko zirimo virusi zisa na SARS-CoV, ariko ntihagaragaye virusi SARS-CoV-2 ikuriramo.
Hagaragaye beta-CoV yo mu gisamujyonjyo isa cyane na SARS-CoV-2, bikerekana ko ibisamujyonjyo bishobora kuba inyamaswa ikuriramo cyangwa beta-CoV yo mu gisamujyonjyo ikaba ari imwe mu bice bya jene byihuza bikavamo SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo hari ibikibazwa, nta gihamya ko SARS-CoV-2 yakozwe n’abantu ku bushake cyangwa ku bw’impanuka.
CoV zongeye kuvugwaho bitewe ni uko haherutse kwaduka icyorerezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Ubushakashatsi kuri CoV yo mu ducurama n’izindi nyamaswa bwahinduye cyane imyumvire yacu yerekeye inyamaswa zibamo HCoV mu kwanduza abantu.
Ibimenyetso bikomeye bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zikomoka ku gacurama maze zikanduzwa abantu binyuze mu nyamaswa zikuriramo.
Kuba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV buturuka mu kwegerena kw’abantu n’impimbi mu masoko abagirwamo inyamaswa, kuyafunga no kwica impimbi ziyarimo byari guhagarika neza icyorezo cya SARS.
Ni na ko ibisamujyonjyo bigomba gukurwa mu masoko abagirwamo inyamaswa mu kwirinda ko byanduza izindi nyamaswa, hakurikijwe ubushakashatsi ku nkomoko ya beta-CoV yo mu bisamujyonjyo ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko uko abantu bandura virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ivuye ku bisamujyonjyo n’izindi nyamabere bigomba gusobanurwa neza mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa.
Ku rundi ruhande, hashize igihe kirekire virusi ya MERS-CoV iba mu ngamiya.
Izo ngamiya ni inyamaswa z’ingenzi mu bwikorezi no gutanga inyama, amata, impu n’ubwoya bukorwamo imyenda ku batuye mu gace zibamo.
Zakwirakwiye cyane mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati n’Afurika.
Bityo, ntawakwigomwa ingamiya zose mu kurwanya virusi ya MERS, nk’ibyakozwe mu masoko abagirwamo inyamaswa mu Bushinwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Mu rwego rwo guhagarika icyorezo cya MERS kigenda kigaruka, hagomba gufatwa ingamba zikomeye hamwe n’izindi ngamba zo kurwanya indwara hagakorwa urukingo rwa virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Mu gihe tudashoboye kurimbura izo virusi, jenotipe nshya zishobora kugaragara maze zigateza ibyorezo.
CoV zitandukanye zifata inyamaswa zizenguruka mu mashyamba.
By’umwihariko, CoV zo mu gacurama zifite ubushobozi butandukanye.
Mu minsi iri imbere, birashoboka cyane ko CoV ifata inyamaswa yahinduka, bigatuma hagaragara ubwoko bushya bwa CoV bwandura cyane cyangwa bwica abantu benshi.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa z’ishyamba mu bice bimwe by’Ubushinwa ugomba gucika hakirindwa kwegerana kw’abantu n’inyamaswa bitari ngombwa.
Hakurikijwe ibibazo bikomeje guterwa na SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hakenewe gahunda isobanutse yo kurwanya izo virusi.
Muri make, ku isi hagiye habaho virusi nyinshi kuva kera.
Ziguma mu nyamaswa zisanzwe zibamo kugeza zibonye amahirwe yo gusohoka.
Nubwo uducurama dufite imiterere myinshi ituma dukwirakwiza virusi, ibyago by’uko abantu bahura n’uducurama n’andi moko y’inyamaswa z’ishyamba bishobora kugabanywa igihe abantu bigishijwe kutabyegera.
Gukomeza gukurikirana inyamabere ni ngombwa mu kurushaho gusobanukirwa ubuturo bwa CoV n’inyamaswa ikuriramo, bikaba ingirakamaro mu kwirinda ko inyamaswa zakwanduza abantu no gukumira ibyorezo by’ahazaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bunoze bwo gukumira virusi zo mu nyamaswa ni uko abantu bakwiye kutegera ubutor bw’izo virusi n’inyamaswa zikuriramo.
Haracyari amoko menshi y’inyamaswa virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ikomokaho ataramenyekana.
Icya mbere, niba uducurama twanduza ibisamujyonjyo virusi yabyaye SARS-CoV-2, birashishikaje kureba igituma uducurama n’ibisamujyonjyo biba mu buturo bumwe.
Icya kabiri, niba uducurama twanduza abantu virusi mu buryo butaziguye, uko abantu bahura n’uducurama bikwiye kugaragazwa.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamabere ya gatatu ikora nk’inyamaswa ikuriramo koko, ni gute ibana n’amoko y’inyamaswa atandukanye twavuga nk’abantu, uducurama n’ibisamujyonjyo bigomba gusobanuka.
Hanyuma, mu gihe inyamabere nyinshi harimo inyamaswa zororerwa mu rugo zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, kuzikurikirana no kureba uko zandura indwara bigomba gukorwa.
Abaye ari agacurama, igisamujyonjyo cyangwa indi nyamabere, hitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi ziyibyara zijya gusa cyane zizagaragara mu nyamaswa zikuriramo mu gihe kiri imbere.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje kuri izi nyamaswa buzasobanura inzira y’imihindagurikire ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, bikazagira uruhare runini mu kwirinda no kurwanya COVID-19 mu bantu.
Kuvugurura ibigenderwaho mu gusuzuma COVID-19 “abakekwaho uburwayi” n'“abemejwe ko barwaye” ni ngombwa
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryatangaje imirongo ngenderwaho yihuse ikubiyemo inama zo gusuzuma no kuvura indwara ya koronavirusi nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi imirongo ngenderwaho yaduhaye ubunararibonye kandi itanga ibisobanuro byiza byo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Nyamara, indwara ya koroanvirusi 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, imyumvire n'ubumenyi byacu kuri yo bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi burimo gukorwa n'ibikorwa byo mu buvuzi; bityo rero ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura nazo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije igitekerezo kimwe ku murongo ngenderwaho wacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya bigenderwaho mu gusuzuma “ukekwaho uburwayi” n'“abemejwe ko barwaye” dukurikije amabwiriza aheruka yo gusuzuma no kuvura ya COVID-19 (icyiciro cya karindwi) yashyizwe ahagaragara na komite y'igihugu ishinzwe ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y’Ubushinwa.
Mu Kuboza 2019, koronavirusi nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu ku mugaragaro kikaba cyitwa indwara ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yiswe icyorezo cy'ubuhumekero gikomeye cya koronavirusi 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry’Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryashyizeho imirongo ngenderwaho y’inama zihutirwa kandi yatangajwe ku rubuga rwa interineti mu bushakashatsi bw’ubuvuzi bwa Gisirikare ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka yashishikaje abantu benshi.
Ariko ni ngombwa kumenya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, imyumvire yacu n'ubumenyi bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi burimo gukorwa n'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura nazo zikomeza kuvugururwa.
Dutanze urugero, Amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komite y'ubuzima yo ku rwego rw'igihugu ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y’Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye ibitabo birindwi harimo bimwe mu bice byahindutse ku buryo bugaragara.
Noneho umurongo ngenderwaho wacu wakiriye igitekerezo cya Zhou n'abandi, batangije uburyo bworoshye bwo gutanga amanota hashingiwe ku byo bahuye nabyo mu buvuzi.
Ibikorwa byabo byongeyeho ibimenyetso bifatika bishya byerekana umurongo ngenderwaho wacu kandi binatanga ibisobanuro by'ingirakamaro kuri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Dushyigikiye umurimo ukomeye bakoze kandi turabibashimiye.
Ariko, ibyo bakoze bigomba kandi kuvugururwa ukurikije amabwiriza aheruka gushyirwaho yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Igerageza ry'icyiciro cya karindwi) ndetse n'ubushakashatsi buherutse.
Nk’uko bigaragara mu gitabo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020) kwemeza abakekwaho uburwayi bigomba guhuzwa na kimwe mu biranga amateka y’ibyorezo n’ibintu bibiri byerekana uburwayi kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa bigomba guhura n’ibintu bitatu byerekana uburwayi niba amateka ajyanye n'ibyorezo adasobanutse:
Amateka ajyanye n'icyorezo: (1) Kuba harabayeho gukorera urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa ahandi hari abarwaye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) Kuba harabaye guhura n'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 (hamwe n'ibipimo bigaragaza ko afite aside nikileyike); (3) Kuba harabaye guhura n’abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by’ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa ahandi hari abarwaye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) kuba harabayeho guhura n'abarwaye biganje mu gace runaka (abarwaye barenze 2 bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka nabi byagaragaye mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 ahantu hato, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri n'ahandi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka nabi; (2) hamwe n'ibimenyetso bigaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) ingano rusange y'uturemangingo twera tw'amaraso tugaragaza umubare watwo usanzwe, utiyongera cyangwa ngo ugabanuke mu cyiciro kibanza.
Gupima uwo byemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira k'ukekwaho uburwayi ugaragaza kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara cyangwa bishingiye ku maraso bikurikira: (1) Igipimo cya PCR cyafashwe mu gihe nyacyo cyagaragaje uburwayi bwa SARS-CoV-2; (2) ikurikirana ry'uduce tw'ingenzi tugize virusi ryerekana ko hari aho ihuriye na koronavirusi nshya tuzi; (3) kugaragaza uburwayi ku turindamubiri twihariye twa IgM na IgG kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu gupima serumu; cyangwa impinduka y'akarindamubiri kihariye IgG ka SARS-CoV-2 kava mu batarwaye kajya mu barwaye, cyangwa ukwiyongerera ahantu hamwe kurenze inshuro 4 mu gice cyo gukira kirenze icyo mu gihe cy'uburwayi bukomeye.
Tubona ko ibipimo by'aside nikileyike mu nzira y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo ngero by'amaraso bifatiwe igihe byongerewe mu gitabo cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Gutahura uburwayi mu bipimo ngero by’amaraso byongewe mu bitabo byasohotse ku nshuro ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bishingiye ku maraso byongerwa ku cyasohotse ku nshuro ya karindwi.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku byakomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi bashakisha uburyo bwiza bwo kumenya aside nikileyike igaragara kugira ngo hakorwe isuzuma ryihuse, ndetse n'ibipimo ngero byo mu nzira y'ubuhumekero harimo ibipimo ngero by'amaraso, ibyo bikaba bituma haboneka ingero zitandukanye, kandi bigashyigikira kuzana uturindamubiri twihariye tw'uwanduye mu bigenderwaho byemejwe.
Uretse ibyo, hari ibimenyetso byinshi cyane bitwibutsa kwitondera abarwayi badasanzwe bafite ibimenyetso n'abatabifite.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, imbonerahamwe ya Zhou n'abandi igomba kuvugururwa, nk'uko bashyize mu byiciro umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk"ibyago bike".
Uburyo bw'amanota nabwo bugomba kugenzurwa mu bindi bikorwa by'ubuvuzi n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu gusoza, turizera ko ibindi bimenyetso bitaziguye bizagaragara kandi turanasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku bijyanye n'isuzuma "ry'abakekwaho indwara" n'"abemejwe ko barwaye", turasaba gukurikirana no kubahiriza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizanavugururira ku gihe imirongo ngenderwaho yacu kugira ngo itange ubufasha.
Bangaladeshi yatangaje ko abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19, ukaba ari wo mubare munini mu munsi umwe
Ejo, Bangaladeshi yemeje ko abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 uwo munsi.
Ni wo mubare munini w'abapfuye mu munsi umwe bishwe n’iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, Ikigo kirwanya ibyorezo, indwara kikanakora ubushakashatsi muri Bangaladeshi (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w’abanduye harimo 114 bakirwaye n’abakize 33 bari bari iwabo.
Igiteranyo cy’abapfuye ni abantu 17.
Mu makuru yatambutse kuri interineti, Umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko muri abo bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n’umugore umwe.
Nk’uko byavuzwe na Dr Meerjady, abapfuye babiri bari bafite imyaka irenga 60, babiri bari bafite hagati y’imyaka 51 na 60 n’umwe wari ufite hagati y’imyaka 41 na 50.
Yanatangaje ko babiri mu bahitanywe n’icyorezo bari baraturutse muri Dhaka.
Ishami ry’Umuryango w’Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe.
