Ubushimusi bw'inyamaswa n'indwara inyamaswa zanduza abantu - Ingaruka z'ubuzima zijyanye n'ubucuruzi bw'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba
Gupimira muri raboratwari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi bijyanye ya SARS-CoV-2 bikubiyemo uburyo bwo gushaka virusi n'uburyo bwo gutahura abasirikare b'umubiri umubiri ukora mu kurwanya indwara.
Kuba virusi ziri mu bizamini byafashwe byemezwa na RT-PCR, itahura RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iki kizamini kirihariye kandi cyagenewe gutahura gusa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Gikoreshwa mu kwemeza abanduye vuba cyangwa abakirwaye.
Gutahura abasirikare b'umubiri (ikizamini cy'amaraso) bishobora gukoreshwa haba mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri byerekana umubare w'abantu barwaye iyo ndwara, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso bito cyane ku buryo bitatuma bamenyesha ababishinzwe ko banduye cyangwa abadafite ibimenyetso.
Umubare nyakuri w'impfu zitewe n'icyorezo n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa mu baturage ushobora kugenwa uhereye ku byavuye muri iki kizamini.
Kubera imibare mike y'abari bamaze gupimwa, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'ubwiganze bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarapimye abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku buryo ibizamini byagiye bikorwa mu bihugu byose.
Iyi mihindagurikire na yo ishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfuye, bikaba bishoboka ko byakabirizwa cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwihuse mu gufata no gusesengura ibipimo by'ubwandu (rRT-PCR), gupima iyi ndwara bishobora gukorerwa ku bizamini byafashwe mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bibonekahakoreshejwe uburyo bunyuranye, burimo ibizamini by'igikororwa cyangwa amatembabuzi yo mu muhogo.
Muri rusange, ibisubizo biboneka hagati y'amasaha make kugeza ku minsi 2.
Ikizamini cya RT-PCR gikorwahafashwe ibipimo byo mu muhogo ni bwo buryo bwonyine bwizewe gusa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma virusi ishobora gushira mu muhogo mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu basuzumwe bagasanga baranduye mu cyumweru cya kabiri, byaba byiza bongeye gufatwa ibindi bizamini bitandukanye hapimwa nk'igikorora.
Kimwe mu bipimo biheruka hifashishijwe PCR cyageragerejwe ahitwa Charité mu mugi wa Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 aho bifashishije uburyo bwihuse mu gufata no gusesengura ibipimo by'ubwandu (rRT-PCR) n'ibikoresho ibihumbi 250 000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima.
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwarateguye ikizamini bitarenze ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Isosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo yitwa Kogenebiotech yateguye igerageza ry'igikoresho cyo kwa muganga cyo gutahura SARS-CoV-2 ishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Ishakisha akaremangingo ka "E" gakwirakwizwa n'ubwoko bwa koronavirusi iba mu mubiri w'umuntu, ndetse n'akaremangingo ka RdRp kagaragara muri SARS-CoV-2. Mu gihugu cy'Ubushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe muri kompanyi za mbere mu kwemererwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe ibikoresho byo mu buvuzi gukoresha ibikoresho bipima SARS –CoV-2 ishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe Z'Amerika, ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no kurwanya ibyorezo (CDC) kirimo gukwirakwiza ibikoresho bya RT-PCR Diagnostic byifashishwa mu gupima Koronavirusi nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV) muri za raboratwari rusange binyujijwe mu kigo cyitwa International Reagent Resource.
Kimwe mu bizamini bitatu byerekana imiterere y'uturemangingo muri verisiyo ya kera y'ibikoresho byifashishwa mu gupima byatumye hatangwa ibisubizo bidasobanutse bitewe n'imiti itujuje ubuziranenge yakoreshejwe, ndetse n'imbogamizi mu gupima ku Kigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara (CDC) muri Atlanta; ibi byatumye impuzandengo y'ibizamini 100 ku munsi bisuzumwa neza muri Gashyantare 2020 yose.
Ibizamini byakoresheje ibice bibiri ntabwo byari biteganyijwe ko byizerwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe ni bwo raboratwari za Leta n'iz'uturere zemerewe gutangira gupima.
Ikizamini cyemejwe n'ubuyobozi bushinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti byemewe n'uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa. Raboratwari z'ubucuruzi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gupima mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje mu gihugu hose ko habonetse uburyo bwo gupima COVID-19 bushingiye kuri RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics nayo yakoze mu gihugu hose ibizamini bya COVID-19 biboneka guhera ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mubare ntarengwa watangajwe; gukusanya no gutunganya ingero zafashwe bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa n'Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara (CDC).
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyateguwe kandi gikorwa n'ikigo cya Leta cy'ubushakashatsi kuri virusi n'ikoranabuhanga mu binyabuzima VECTOR.
Kuwa 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ikigo cya Leta Gishinzwe kwita ku buvuzi cyatangiye gupima iyi virusi. Kuwa 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Ivuriro rya Mayo ryakoze igikoresho gishobora gupima icyorezo cya COVID-19. Kuwa 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yemerewe na FDA gukora imashini yo gupima iyi virusi yagombaga gutanga ibisubizo mu masaha 3,5 ku kigero cyo hejuru, ibi bikaba byaratumaga imashini imwe ishobora gupima abantu 4 128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha ku buryo bwihutirwa (EUA) kuri Raboratwari ya Abbott kugira ngo ikore ikizamini kuri sisitemu ya m2000 ya Abbott; FDA yari yaratanze uburenganzira busa na Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid nayo yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha uburyo bwihutirwa ruvuye muri FDA kugira ngo hakorwe ikizamini kimara iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikizamini gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongera ibipimo by'ubushyuhe kuri aside nikileyiki aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko ibi bidasaba urukurikirane mu guhinduranya ubushyuhe ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo by'uwanduye mu minota mike nk'itanu n'ibisubizo by'utanduye mu minota 13.
Kugeza ubu muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hari imashini z'ubu bwoko zigera kuri 18 000 kandi Abbot iteganya kongera ubushobozi ku buryo ibipimo byagera kuri 50 000 ku munsi. Muri Tayiwani harimo gukorwa Igipimisho gikoresha abasirikare b'umubiri bihuza n'intungamubiri zo mu bwoko bwa N za Koronavirusi, kandi hari ikizere ko gishobora gutanga ibisubizo hagati y'iminota 15 na 20 mbese nk'imashini ipima ibicurane ku buryo bwihuse.
Muri Werurwe 2020, inyandiko z'ubushakashatsi zanzuye ko "mu ntangiriro kunyura mu cyuma harebwa mu gatuza bidafite akamaro cyane mu kwisuzumisha, naho ibyerekanwa n'uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bwa CT [computing tomografiya] bishobora kuba bihari na mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira."
Ibiranga uburyo bw'ikoranabuhanga bwa CT mu kunyuza mu cyuma birimo kubasha kureba impande zose z'ibihaha, bugaragaza neza ku ruhande, hagati ndetse n'igice cy'inyuma.
Akugara k'igice cyo munsi y'ibihaha, kwitsindagira cyane kw'ibice bimwe bigize ibihahaha bigenda byiyongera uko icyorezo kirushaho gukomera.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hagamijwe kugereranya ibyo bipimo bya PCR na CT muri Wuhan hashakishwa inkomoko y'icyo cyorezo bwerekanye ko ibyo bimenyetso bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyari gikomeye cyane i Wuhan kuko ho kivanze n'izindi ndwara zibasira imyanya y'ubuhumekero kurushaho.
Kugera mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, Ishuri rikuru ry'Ubuvuzi bwo kunyuza mu cyuma muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ryategetse ko "Uburyo bukoreshwa i Wuhan butakongera gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma KoronavirusiCOVID-19". Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara (CDC) gisaba ko PCR ari yo yakoreshwa mu kwisuzumisha mbere.
Bumwe mu buryo bw'ubudahangarwa umubiri ushyiraho urwanya ubwandu ni ugukora abasirikare b'umubiri barimo IgM na IgG.
Ibi byafasha mu kuvumbura ubwandu mu bantu guhera ku munsi wa 7 cyangwa nyuma yo kubona ibimenyetso by'ibanze,mu kureba ingano y'ubwirinzi no gukora igenzura mu baturage. Isesengura ry'ibipimo rishobora gukorerwa muri raboratwari zisanzwe (CLT) cyangwa ahandi hantu hagenewe gupimira ( PoCT).
Uburo bukoreshwa mu gupima abantu benshi muri raboratwari nyinshi zo kwa muganga, buzakoreshwa mu gusesengura, ariko kuboneka kw'ibisubizo bizaterwa n'umuvuduko w'imikorere.
Muri raboratwari zisanzwe, urugero rumwe rw'amaraso yafashwe ni rwo rusanzwe rukoreshwa, n'ubwo ingero zikurikirana zishobora gukoreshwa hagamijwe gukurikirana ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri.
Ku handi hantu hagenewe gupimirwa, urugero rumwe rw'amaraso rusanzwe ruboneka habayeho gutobora uruhu.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, uburyo bwo kubanza kuvoma ibigomba gupimwa ntabwo bukenewe mbere yo gupima. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatangaje ibigo 29 byayimenyesheje nk'uko bisabwa noneho bikaba bishobora gutanga ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri byakoze.
Guhera ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ikizamini kimwe gusa ni cyo cyemejwe na FDA ko kigomba gukorwa babiherewe uburenganzira igihe byihutirwa.Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostic byahawe ibyemezo by'Iburayi ku bikoresho byabo byo gupima, bishobora kumenya abasirikare b'umubiri ba IgG na IgA mu kurwanya virusi mu bizamini by'amaraso.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima ubwandu bushobora kugera ku bizamini amagana bisuzumwa mu masaha noneho bikihuta cyane ugereranyije n'ikizamini cya PCR cyari gisanzwe gikoreshwa cyo gupima RNA iterwa na virusi.
Ubusanzwe abasirikare b'umubiri bagaragara mu minsi 14 nyuma y'uko ubwandu butangiye. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwasanze nta bikoresho bipima ingano y'abasirikare b'umubiri bwaguze nta na kimwe gishobora gukoreshwa ku buryo buhagije.
Hongukongo yashyizeho uburyo umuntu wese uketsweho ubwandu ashobora kuguma mu rugo, ishami rishinzwe ubutabazi rikamuha "agakoresho kabugenewe", agaciramo hanyuma akakabasubiza bakazamuha igisubizo nyuma. Serivisi zishinzwe ubuzima mu Bwongereza (NHS) zatangaje ko ziteganya gushyiraho uburyo bwo gupimira mu rugo abantu bakekwaho ubwandu, ibi bikazakuraho ibyago byo kuba umurwayi ashobora kwanduza abandi igihe baje mu bitaro, cyangwa se hakaba hasabwa gutera imiti yica udukoko twanduza indwara mu modoka yazanye umurwayi. Mu gikorwa cyo gufata ibizamini by'uwaketsweho COVID-19, umuganga abikora mu buryo bwa kinyamwuga yubahiriza amabwiriza yose.
Ahantu ho gupimira abantu bari mu binyabiziga byabo hafashije Koreya y'Epfo gukora bimwe mu bizamini byihuta cyane, kandi byinshi cyane kurusha ibindi bihugu. Mu Budage, ku ya 2 Werurwe, Ishyirahamwe ry'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bw'abaganga ryatangaje, ko rifite ubushobozi bwo gupima hafi 12,000 ku munsi hakoreshejwe imbangukiragutabara kandi abagera ku 10 700 barapimwe mu cyumweru kibanziriza iki.
Ibiciro byishyurwa n'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima mu gihe ikizamini gitegekwa na muganga.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na perezida w'ikigo cya Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi rusange bwo gupima abantu 160 000 buri cyumweru.
Kuva ku ya 19 Werurwe uburyo bwo gupima bwakorewe mu mijyi minini myinshi.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 umubare rusange w'ibizamini byakorewe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi, kubera ko havuzwe gusa abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe na raboratwari bwatangaje ko mu cyumweru cya 12/2020 hari hamaze gupimwa abantu bagera nibura kuri 483 295 ubariyemo n'icyumeru cya 12/2020, muri bo abagera kuri 33 491 (6,9%) basanganywe SARS-CoV-2. Muri Isiraheli, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam bavumbuye kandi bagerageza uburyo bwo gupima abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, aho bafata ibizamini bakaza kongera kubipima nyuma iyo hari uwo basanganye uburwayi. Muri Wuhan, raboratwari y'ubutabazi ifite ubuso bwa m2 2000 yitwa "Huo-Yan" 火眼 mu Gishinwa, cyangwa "Ijisho ry'umuriro" mu Kinyarwanda, yafunguwe ku mugaragaro kuwa 5 Gashyantare 2020 n'ikigo cyitwa BGI, ishobora gupima abantu barenga 10 000 ku munsi.
Imirimo yo kubaka yagenzuwe n'uwashinze BGI, Wang Jian kandi yamaze igihe cy'iminsi 5, ingero zafashwe zerekanye ko ubwandu muri Hubei bwari kwiyongeraho 47% kandi ikiguzi cyo guhangana n'abari gushyirwa mu kato cyari kwikuba kabiri iyo ubu bushobozi bwo gupima butaboneka.
Raboratwari ya Wuhan yahise ikurikirwa na raboratwari za Huo-Yanmu Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, na Shanghai, mu mijyi 12 yose mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, muri rusange hakorwa ibipimo 50 000 ku munsi. Uburyo bwihuse kandi bushobora gukoreshwa na buri wese bwashyizwe ahagaragara na Origami Assays bushobora gupima ibizamini by'abarwayi 1 122 ba COVID19 hakoreshejwe ibipimo 93 gusa.  Ubu buryo bugererenyije bushobora gukorerwa muri raboratwari ntoya bitabaye ngombwa kwitabaza robo zitunganya ibisukika.
Kugeza muri Werurwe, kugabanuka ndetse no kubura imiti y'ingezi yo muri raboratwari byabaye imbogamizi ikomeye mu gupima abantu benshi mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi, Ubwongereza na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ibi byatumye abanditsi bamwe bandika ku myiteguro y'ifatwa ry'ibizamini aho bisaba kubishyushya kugera kuri 98 °C (208 °F) mu gihe cy'iminota 5 kugira ngo hagaragare uturemangingo dutuma bongera gupima. Ku wa 31 Werurwe hatangajwe ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu zari ku mwanya wa mbere mu kugira ubushobozi bwo gupima umubare munini w'abaturage bazo ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu, iki gihugu kikaba cyari gifite gahunda yo gupima abaturage hafi ya bose bagituye.
Ibi byatewe no guhuriza hamwe ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bari mu modoka zabo, no kugura raboratwari zishobora gupima abantu benshi icyarimwe muri Group 42 na BGI (hashingiwe kuri raboratwari za Huo-Yan zipima ku buryo bwihuse).
Yubatswe mu minsi 14, raboratwari ishobora gukora ibizamini ibihumbi birenga icumi bya RT-PCR ku munsi kandi ni yo ya mbere ku isi yo kuri uri rwego ikorera hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo gupima bureba ibice bitandukanye bigize imiterere y'ibiranga koronavirusi bwashyizweho mu Bushinwa, Ubufaransa, Ubudage, Hongukongo, Ubuyapani, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje uburyo bwatanzwe n'Ubudage bwo gukora ibikoresho byoherejwe mu bihugu bikennye bidafite amikoro yo kwikorera ibyabyo.
Kuwa 17 Mutarama 2020, Abadage batangaje uburyo bwabo, uburyo bwari bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kugenzura indwara ntibwari bukiboneka kugera kuwa 28 Mutarama, ibi bikaba byaratumaga ibipimo bitinda muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika. Ubushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika bari bafite ibibazo bijyanye no kutizera ubuziranenge bw'ibikoresho byo gupima byari bihari, kandi ibi bihugu kimwe na Ositaraliya nta bushobozi bwo guhaza isoko ry'ibyo bikoresho byari bifite ndetse no kubahiriza inama zatangwaga n'inzobere mu buvuzi.
Ariko, impuguke zivuga ko kuba Koreya y'Epfo yarashyizeho uburyo bwagutse bwo gupima byafashije mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi nshya ya koronavirusi.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima, cyane cyane muri za raboratwari z'abigenga, bwubatswe mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi na Leta ya Koreya y'Epfo.
Kuwa 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryahamagariye amahanga kongera umubare w'ibipimo na gahunda zijyanye n'icyo gikorwa kuko ari bwo buryo bwiza bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19. Kuba ibikoresho bipima icyorezo byararushijeho gukenerwa n'abantu benshi kubera ikwirakwira rya virusi, byatumye byinshi muri byo byiharirwa na za raboratwari zo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, hahita havuka ikibazo gikomeye cyo kugeza ku bantu ibikoresho n'imiti bikenewe mu buvuzi bw'iki cyorezo.
Muri Werurwe 2020 Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko hari ibibazo bijyanye n'ubuziranenge bw'ibikoresho byabwo byo gupima.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho byakozwe n'Ikigo k'Igihugu gishinzwe kugenzura indwara byari bifite inenge, noneho Leta ikuraho imbogamizi zabuzaga gukora isuzuma ryigenga. Esipanye yaguze ibikoresho muri Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Co Ltd, ikigo cyo mu Bushinwa ariko yasanze bitujuje ubuziranenge.
Icyo kigo cyasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari ukuri bishobora guterwa no kudakusanya neza ibizamini cyangwa kudakoresha neza ibikoresho.
Minisiteri yo muri Esipanye yavuze ko bazakura ku isoko ibikoresho bitanga ibisubizo bitari byo kandi bikazasimbuzwa ibyakozwe n'ikigo cya Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'ibikoresho igihugu cya Ceke cyaguze mu Bushinwa byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo.Silovakiya yaguze mu Bushinwa ibikoresho miriyoni 1,2 basanga bitujuje ubuziranenge.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovič yifuje ko byajugunywa mu mugezi witwa Danube. Ateş Kara, Minisitiri w'Ubuzima muri Turikiya yavuze ko ibikoresho bikoreshwa mu gusuzuma byaguzwe mu Bushinwa bitujuje ubuziranenge bityo ko bitagomba gukoreshwa. Ubwongereza bwaguze mu Bushinwa, ibikoresho miriyoni 3,5 byo gupima ariko vuba aha mu kwezi kwa Mata 2020 batangaje ko bitabasha gukoreshwa.
Gupima, bikurikiwe no gushyira mu kato abanduye ndetse no gushakisha abahuye n'abanduye SARS-CoV-2, byatanze umusaruro.
Abashakashatsi bakora mu mujyi wa Vò wo mu Butaliyani, ahapfiriye bwa mbere umurwayi wa COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, bapimye inshuro ebyiri abaturage bose bagera ku 3 400, mu ntera y'igihe cy'iminsi icumi.
Hafi y'icya kabiri cy'abasanze banduye nta bimenyetso bagaragazaga, kandi abagaragaraye bose bashyizwe mu kato.
Guhagarika ingendo zigana mu tundi turere, byahagaritse burundu ubwandu bushya bw'icyorezo.
Kubera igenzura rikarishye ryo gukurikirana abahuye n'ubwandu, gukumira urujya n'uruza rw'abantu, gufata ibipimo no gushyira mu kato, ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2020 muri Singapuru bwabaye buke cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere kandi bikaba byarakozwe hadafunzwe burundu za resitora n'inzu z'ubucuruzi.
Ibikorwa byinshi byarahagaritswe, kandi Singapuru yatangiye igira inama abaturage kuguma mu rugo ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura ku gihe nyuma y'ibiruhuko ku ya 23 Werurwe.
Ibihugu byinshi kandi byahanganye n'iki cyorezo bishyiraho uburyo bwo gushakisha abahuye n'abanduye, gukumira ingendo zo mu gihugu imbere, gupima, gushyira mu kato, no kuguma mu rugo ariko bidakabije cyane, nko muri Ayisilandi na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byapimye abantu benshi, ugereranije n'umubare w'impfu, bifite umubare muto w'abapfa, wenda kubera ko ibyo bihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kumenya abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima risaba ko ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima ndetse bidafite na raboratwari zihagije kandi zifite ubushobozi bwo gupima COVID-19 ko byakohereza ibizamini byabyo by'abantu batanu ba mbere bagaragaye ko banduye n'abantu icumi ba mbere byagaragaye ko batanduye COVID-19 muri raboratwari 16 z'icyitegererezo z'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima kugira ngo ibyo bipimo byemezwe.
Muri raboratwari 16 z'icyitegererezo, 7 ziri muri Aziya, 5 mu Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru indi 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, ahanditse "Abanduye nk'ijanisha % ry'abapimwe" hashobora guhinduka bitewe na politiki y'igihugu yo gupima indwara.
Igihugu gipima abantu bashyizwe mu bitaro gusa kizagira ijanisha riri hejuru ry'abanduye mu bapimwe, ugereranyije n'igihugu gipima abaturage bose, baba bagaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa batabigaragaza, niba nta kindi gihindutse.
Gukaraba intoki, ari na byo bizwi nko gusukura intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gusukura ibiganza hagamijwe gukuraho ibitaka, amavuta, mikorobe, cyangwa ibindi bintu bitifuzwa.
Gukaraba intoki ku buryo buhoraho mu "bihe by'ingenzi" ku manywa birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi nk'impiswi, kolera, zandura binyuze mu nzira y'umusarani-mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa giripe isanzwe, urugero, niba batakarabye intoki mbere yo kwikora mu maso, ku mazuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga, ingingo zigira ururenda).
Mu bihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku manywa aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo kwituma, nyuma yo guheha umwana cyangwa kumuhindurira ibyahi, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gufata inyama mbisi, amafi, cyangwa inkoko.
Niba amazi n'isabune bitabonetse, intoki zishobora gusukurwa hakoreshejwe ivu. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima risaba abantu gukaraba intoki:
Mbere yo gutegura amafunguro, mu gihe uyategura na nyuma y'aho.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindurira umwana ibyahi cyangwa nyuma yo gusukura umwana umaze gukoresha umusarani.
Nyuma yo kwipfuna, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku itungo, kurigaburira, cyangwa nyuma yo gusukura umwanda waryo.
Isuku y'intoki mu buvuzi bivuga ibikorwa by'isuku bijyanye n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga umuti cyangwa mbere yo kwita ku murwayi bishobora kurinda cyangwa bikagabanya cyane gukwirakwira kw'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ugusukura intoki zaba zagiyeho indwara (bagiteri, virusi, cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'imiti ishobora gutera ingaruka cyangwa indwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bategura ibiribwa cyangwa abakora mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, ariko ni n'umuco mwiza ukwiye kuranga abantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki bifite inyungu nyinshi mu rwego rw'ubuzima, zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi, n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo; kurinda izindi mpamvu zatera indwara y'impiswi; kugabanya indwara zo myanya y'ubuhumekero;
kandi bigabanya ijanisha ry'imfu z'abana bavukira mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza bishobora kugira uruhare mu mikurire myiza y'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impfu z'abana ziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'impiswi zishobora kugabanuka hifashishijwe uburyo bworoshye bwo guhindura imyitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune.
Ubu buryo bworoshye bushobora kugabanya igipimo cy'impfu ziterwa n'izi ndwara hafi kuri 50%.
Ibikorwa bishishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya nka kimwe cya gatatu cy'indwara z'impiswi kandi ibi ni kimwe no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dutuwemo n'abafite imibereho iciriritse.
Kugabanuka kw'indwara zifitanye isano n'impiswi ku kigero cya 48% bishobora guhuzwa no gukaraba hakoreshejwe isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwiza cyane bwonyine kandi budahenze mu kwirinda impiswi n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikaze (ARI), bikaba bigomba kuba umugenzo mu ngo, ku ishuri no mu muryango mugari.
Umusonga, Indwara y'Ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane, ni yo iri ku isonga mu guhitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, ihitana ubuzima bw'abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1,8 ku mwaka.
Impiswi n'umusonga byombi bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
Hashingiwe ku bitangazwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumye ryita ku Bana (UNICEF), gukoresha isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo gukoresha umusarani ku buryo buhoraho bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kuruta urukingo urwo ari rwo rwose cyangwa ubundi buryo bwo kwivuza, kandi byagabanyaho hafi kimwe cya kabiri ku mpfu ziterwa n'impiswi ndetse na kimwe cya kane cy'impfu ziterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikabije.
Akenshi gukaraba intoki biba biri mu bindi bikorwa by'isuku bigize gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isukura (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda kandi indwara itera amabara ku ruhu yandura binyuze mu gukoranaho n'abandi.
Ingaruka ntoya yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera uruhu kwangirika kubera kuma cyane kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe muri Danimarike mu 2012 bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki birenze urugero bishobora gutera uburibwe, gukomera kw'uruhu bikunze kwitwa indwara z'uruhu rwo ku ntoki, ikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakozi bashinzwe ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki cyane nabyo bigaragara nka kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'imyitwarire idahwitse yo gutinya indwara (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku manywa aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara bunyura mu musarani no mu kanwa: nyuma yo gukoresha umusarani (kwihagarika, kwituma), nyuma yo guheha umwana (kumuhindurira ibyahi), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gufata inyama mbisi, amafi, cyangwa inkoko.
Ahandi hakwiye gukoreshwa uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo hirindwe kwandura indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igisebe; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora, cyangwa kwipfuna; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'inyamaswa cyangwa kwita ku nyamaswa; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, hari igipimo cyo ku rwego rwo hasi mu gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki bwakorewe mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ku mpuzandengo 38,7% by'ingo zakoresheje isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo cyo hejuru kingana na 97%; Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zifite hafi ya 77%; naho Ubushinwa bukagira igipimo cyo hasi kingana na 23%. Muri iki gihe hariho uburyo bwo guhindura imyumvire mu rwego rwo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune mu bihe bikomeye. Gukarabira intoki icyarimwe ku bana bakiri mu ishuri ku nshuro zagenwe ku munsi ni bumwe mu buryo bushobora gukoreshwa mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu rwego rwo gutoza abana umuco wo gukaraba intoki.
Gahunda y'Ingenzi yo kwita ku Buzima yashyizwe mu bikorwa n'Ishami ry'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rwiza rw'ibikorwa bigamije guteza imbere ubuzima bw'abana n'uburezi.
Gufata imiti y'inzoka zo mu nda inshuro ebyiri mu mwaka, bifatanyije no gukaraba intoki buri munsi ukoresheje isabune, koza amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fuliwore, ni ryo shingiro ry'iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Yashyizwe mu bikorwa neza muri Indoneziya.
Kuvana mikorobe ku ruhu byongerwa imbaraga no kongera mu mazi amasabune cyangwa imiti y'isuku.
Akamaro gakomeye k'amasabune n'imiti y'isuku ni kugabanya ibibuza kuyonga no kongera ubushobozi bwo kuyonga.
Amazi yonyine ntasukura neza uruhu kubera amavuta n'ibinure, bisa n'ibigize ubutaka, bidapfa gushonga mu mazi.
Gukora isuku, bijyana no gukoresha amazi ahagije..
Amasabune atari ay'amazi, bitewe n'uko ashobora kongera gukoreshwa, ashobora kugumana udukoko twanduza indwara yavuye ku bayakoresheje mbere.
Umubare muto w'ubushakashatsi wasuzumye uburyo bwo kwanduza k'udukoko twanduza indwara zivuye mu isabune yanduye maze hanzurwa ko kwanduzwabidashoboka kuko utwo dukoko twanduza tuba twahanaguwe n'ifuro.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara (CDC) kiracyavuga ko "isabune y'amazi hamwe n'aho kuyikoreshereza hadasaba ko ukoraho uyisohora ari bwo buryo bwiza".
Isabune yica udukoko twanduza indwara yashimiwe cyane abantu bashishikajwe no kwita ku buzima bwabo.
Kugeza ubu, nta kimenyetso cyerekana ko gukoresha imiti irinda ubwandu cyangwa imiti yica udukoko duhitamo imiti ihangana n'udukoko tuzwiho kwihanganira imiti yica bagiteri.
Nyamara, amasabune yica udukoko twanduza arimo imiti yica udukoko nka triclosan, ifite urutonde runini rw'udukoko tudapfa guhangarwa.
Bityo rero, nubwo imiti irinda ubwandu bw'indwara itatoranyijwe mu miti y'isabune zica udukoko twanduza, ishobora kuba idakora neza cyane nk'uko yamamazwa.
Usibye kuba yarinda ahantu hadatwikiriye ndetse n'uruhu, iyo miti ishobora kuba irimo za aside (aside asetike, aside asikorbike, aside lakitiki) nko kuringaniza ingano ya Idolojene, aside benzoyike irwanya udukoko twanduza indwara n'izindi zirinda uruhu (igikakarubamba, intungamubiri, menthol, n'indi miti ikomoka ku bimera). Ubusesenguzi bwimbitse bwakozwe na Kaminuza y'Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rusange rya Oregon bwagaragaje ko amasabune asanzwe afite ubushobozi bwo kurinda indwara no gukura ku ntoki udukoko twanduza indwara ku rwego rumwe n'amasabune yagenewe kurwanya udukoko twanduza indwara.
Amazi ashyushye ashobora gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo aba ashyushye bihagije kugira ngo yice udukoko twanduza indwara.
udukoko twanduza indwara dukura vuba cyane ku gipimo cy'ubushyuhe bw'umubiri (37 ° C).
Nyamara, amazi ashyushye, arimo isabune afite akamaro kuruta amazi akonje, arimo isabune mu gukuraho amavuta karemano afite ubutaka n'udukoko twanduza.
Bitandukanye n'uko abantu benshi babyemera, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwerekanye ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye ntacyo bimara mu kugabanya ingano ya mikorobe ku ntoki.
Umuti usukura intoki cyangwa umuti urinda ubwandu bw'intoki ni umuti w'isuku y'intoki utarimo amazi.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21 gukaraba intoki hifashishije imiti yagenewe kwica udukoko twanduza indwara (isanzwe izwi nk'imiti yo gusukura intoki irimo arukoro) byatangiye kumenyekana no gukundwa n'abantu benshi.
Inyinshi iba ikozwe muri arukoro ya "isopropyl" cyangwa "ethanol" ikorwa havanzwe ibyo bita Carbomer mu mavuta buzi cyangwa yongera ubuhehere nka giriserini ikabihinduramo ibisukika cyangwa ifuro mu rwego rwo koroshya ikoreshwa ryayo no kugabanya ingaruka z'arukoro zituma umuntu yumagana.
Kongeramo Idolojene-peroxide ifunguye byongera ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe. Imiti isukura intoki irimo nibura 60 kugera kuri 95% by'arukoro, ishobora gukora neza mu kwica mikorobe.
Imiti yo gusukura intoki irimo arukoro yica udukoko twanduza indwara, udukoko duhangana n'imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, n'izindi virusi (zirimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, rinovirusi, vakisiniya, ibicurane, na hepatite) ndetse na virusi itera ibimeme.
Imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki ifite 70% yica 99,97% (3,5 by'igabanuka, bingana n'igabanuka rya desibeli 35) y'udukoko two ku ntoki mu masegonda 30 nyuma yo kuwukoresha na 99,99% kugera kuri 99,999% (igabanuka riri hagati ya 4 na 5) y'udukoko two ku ntoki nyuma y'umunota 1 nyuma yo gukoreshwa. Imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki ikora neza cyane mu kurwanya udukoko twanduza indwara ariko ikaba idafite ubushobozi bwinshi bwo kurwanya za virusi.
Imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki isa nkaho nta bushobozi ifite bwo kurwanya norovirusi (Norwalk) ikunze gutera indwara z'igifu. Imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki igomba gukoreshwa ku buryo itosa cyangwa ikwira ku biganza byombi.
Imbere n'inyuma h'ibiganza no hagati no ku mpera h'intoki zose harakubwa hafi mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 kugeza amazi, ifuro cyangwa umuti usukura byumye.
Ni ngombwa gukaraba neza imitwe y'intoki uyikubira hamwe mu biganza byombi. Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira ibyorezo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gisaba abantu gukaraba bakoresheje imiti yica udukoko mu biganza cyane cyane iyo bigaragara ko ibiganza byanduye.
Gukomeza gukoresha ubu buryo bishingiye ku kuba bworoshye gukoresha no kuba bwica vuba udukoko twanduza; gusa, ubu buryo ntibukwiye gusimbura uburyo bwagenwe bwo gukaraba intoki keretse mu gihe isabune n'amazi bidahari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti isukura intoki irimo arukoro bishobora gutuma uruhu rwuma keretse muri iyo miti hongewemo iyo koroshya uruhu cyangwa ituma rudakanyarara.
Uko kuma kw'uruhu bitewe na arukoro bishobora kugabanyuka cyangwa bikavanwaho na giliseline cyangwa undi muti woroshya uruhu.
Mu bushakashatsi bwo kwa muganga, imiti isukura intoki irimo arukoro ariko ikanabamo umuti woroshya uruhu ituma uruhu rudakomera cyane kurusha amasabune cyangwa imiti yica mikorobe.
Gufurutwa kw'uruhu, kuzana uduheri cyangwa kwivumbagatanya k'umubiri bitewe n'arukoro iri mu muti usukura intoki bibaho gake.
Kuba hari ibyago bike byo kwangiza uruhu bituma ubu buryo bukoreshwa cyane ugereranije no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune n'amazi.
N'ubwo bikora neza, ibisukura intoki bitarimo amazi ntibisukura intoki ngo bimareho umwanda wose, ahubwo bikuraho udukoko twanduza gusa.
Niyo mpamvu rero umuti wo gusukura intoki udakora neza nk'isabune n'amazi mu kurinda ikwirakwizwa rya virusi nyinshi, kubera ko virusi ikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Imikorere myiza y'imiti isukura intoki itarimo arukoro ishingiye cyane cyane ku biyigize, kandi kera yahoze idakora neza nk'arukoro n'ibindi bisiga bikomoka kuri arukoro.
Vuba aha, imiti ikoresha chloride ya benzalkonium yagaragaje ko ifite ubushobozi buhoraho bwo guhangana na mikorobe nyuma yo kuyikoresha, bitandukanye n'arukoro, byagaragaye ko umusaruro itanga ugenda ugabanuka nyuma yo kuyikoresha inshuro nyinshi, bitewe wenda n'ingaruka igenda igira ku ruhu.
Abantu benshi mu bafite imibereho iciriritse ntibashobora kubona isabune bityo bagakoresha ivu cyangwa itaka.
Gukoresha ivu cyangwa itaka ni ubundi buryo bwiza buruta gukoresha amazi gusa, ariko nanone si bwiza cyane nko gukoresha isabune.
Impungenge imwe ihari ni uko ivu cyangwa itaka bigizwe n'utunyabuzima duto cyane dushobora kwanduza bityo bikaba byakongera ikwirakwizwa ry'icyorezo kurusha uko byarigabanya.
Kimwe n'isabune, ivu naryo ryica udukoko twanduza kubera ko iyo rihuye n'amazi rikora aside.
Mu gihe isabune itabonetse, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima risaba ko hakoreshwa ivu cyangwa umusenyi.
Uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwizwa ry'iki cyorezo ni ubu bukurikira:
Tosa intoki ukoresheje amazi akonje cyangwa ashyushe kandi atemba.
Amazi atemba ni yo agomba gukoreshwa kuko amazi ari mu ibase ashobora kubamo ubwandu, kandi igipimo cy'ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntacyo gihindura cyane.
Karaba intoki zizeho ifuro, uzikuba cyane ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, ukarabe inyuma y'ikiganza, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'inzara.
Isabune ikura ku ruhu udukoko dutera indwara, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakaraba neza intoki iyo bakoresheje isabune kurusha uko bakaraba bakoresheje amazi gusa.
Kuba intoki nibura mu gihe cy'amasegonda 20.
Gutsirita intoki cyane bituma habaho kwikubanaho, bigafasha mu gukura ku ruhu udukoko twanduza indwara, kandi kuzikuba cyane bikuraho utwo dukoko twinshi.
Tosa neza intoki ukoresheje amazi atemba.
Gutohereza intoki mu ibase bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Umutsa intoki ukoresheje igitambaro gisukuye cyangwa uzumutse ukoresheje umwuka.
Intoki zitose cyangwa zitumutse neza zishobora kongera kwandura ku buryo bworoshye. Ahantu hakunze kwibagirana ni ku gikumwe, mu bujana, mu mwanya uri hagati y'intoki, ndetse no munsi y'inzara zo ku ntoki.
Inzara z'inkorano cyangwa inzara ziteye amabara zishobora kuba indiri ya za mikorobe.
Amavuta y'amazi yo koroshya uruhu ni yo abantu basabwa gukoresha kugira ngo intoki zidakanyarara; uruhu rwumye cyane rushobora kwangirika kandi ibyo bikongera ibyago byo gukwirakwira kw'icyorezo.
Hari ubundi buryo buciriritse bushobora gukoreshwa mu rwego rwo koroshya igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki mu gihe uburyo bwo gukoresha robine cyangwa isabune budahari, urugero nko gusuka amazi hakoreshejwe ijerikani imanitse ku giti (kandagirukarabe) cyangwa se igicuma kirimo imyenge yabugenewe cyangwa hagakoreshwa ivu igihe bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu gihe hari ibibazo by'amazi (nko ku bigo by'amashuri cyangwa mu bice by'icyaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo gufata amazi nka kandagirukarabe n'ubundi buryo buhendutse.
Kandagirukarebe ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye rikoresha ijagi imanitse ku mugozi, isuka amazi hakoreshejwe ikirenge, ugakaraba amazi make make mu ntoki n'isabune.
Kumutsa intoki mu buryo bukwiye ni igice cy'ingenzi cyane mu kugirira isuku intoki, ariko ubu haracyari impaka ku buryo bwiza cyane bwakoreshwa mu kumutsa intoki mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko impapuro zikoreshwa mu kwihanagura ziba zifite isuku cyane kurusha ibyuma byumutsa intoki bikoresha amashanyarazi biri mu bwiherero bwinshi.
Mu 2008, Kaminuza ya Westminster i Londere itewe inkunga n'uruganda rukora uduhanaguzo rwitwa "The European Tissue Symposium", yakoze ubushakashatsi bugamije kugereranya ikigero cy'isuku itangwa n'uduhanaguzo, utwumutsantoki n'akuma kagezweho kumutsa intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumutsa intoki ukoresheje icyuma cyumutsa intoki gikoresheje umwuka ushyushye, byagaragaye ko ingano rusange y'udukoko dutera indwara yiyongera ku mpuzandengo ya 194% ahashyirwa intoki ndetse no hagati mu kiganza ku mpuzandengo 254%.
Kumutsa intoki ukoresheje icyuma gihuha umwuka byatumye ingano rusange y'udukoko dutera indwara yiyongera ku mpuzandengo ya 42% ahashyirwa intoki ndetse no hagati mu kiganza ku mpuzandengo 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzumutsa hakoreshejwe impapuro zabugenewe, umubare wose w'agakoko wagabanyijweho ku mpuzandengo ya 76% ku duhanagurantoki no kuri 77% ku biganza. Abahanga kandi bakoze ubushakashatsi kugira ngo barebe niba habaho kwanduzanya hagati y'abantu bakoresha ubwogero ndetse n'ahabukikije bitewe na buri bwoko bw'uburyo bwo kumutsa.
Agakoresho kumutsa, ka kandi gasohora umwuka ku gipimo cy'umuvuduko wa 180m/s (650km/h; 400mph), kashoboraga gukura ku ntoki n'ibindi bice udukoko twanduza ndetse n'ubushobozi bwo kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwogero ndetse no kwigizayo utwo dukoko mu ntera igera kuri metero 2.
Gukoresha icyuma cyumutsa intoki gikoresheje umwuka ushyushye bitumura mikorobe kugeza muri metero 0.25 uvuye aho icyuma kiri.
Uduhanaguzo dukoze mu mpapuro twagaragaje ko tudakwirakwiza cyane mikorobe.Mu 2005, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, hasuzumwe uburyo bunyuranye bwo kumutsa intoki.
Impinduka zikurikira zagaragaye mu mubare w'udukoko twanduza indwara nyuma yo kumutsa intoki:
Hariho abakora ibikoresho byo kumutsa intoki benshi, kandi ibikoresho byumatsa intoki byagereranyijwe n'impapuro z'isuku zumutsa intoki.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti wabugenewe usukura intoki ni ubundi buryo bwakoreshwa mu gihe umuntu ari mu rugendo adafite amazi n'isabune.
Arukoro yagenewe gusukura intoki igomba kuba igizwe nibura na 60% by'arukoro.
Gukaraba intoki kwa muganga byabaye itegeko nyuma y'uko umuganga wo muri Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumburiye akamaro kabyo (muri 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho by'ikoronabuhanga byibutsa abakozi bo kwa muganga gukaraba intoki iyo babyibagiwe.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kubikoresha byagabanyije igipimo cy'ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bimara nibura amasegonda 15, hakoreshejwe isabune nyinshi n'amazi cyangwa umuti wabugenewe utuma haboneka ifuru maze ugakubira hamwe ibiganza byombi.
Intoki zigomba gukubirwa hamwe zinyuranamo ku buryo bwegeranye cyane.
Niba hari umwanda munsi y'inzara, uburoso bwabigenewe bushobora kuwukuramo.
Kuko udukoko twanduza indwara tuguma mu mazi ari ku ntoki, ni ngombwa gutosa neza no kumutsa cyane intoki ukoresheje igitambaro gisukuye.
Nyuma yo kumutsa intoki, agahanaguzo gakozwe mu mpapuro kagomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (ndetse no gufungura umuryango usohoka niba ari ngombwa).
Ibi birinda intoki kongera kwanduzwa n'aho zakoze.
Impamvu yo gukaraba intoki ahatangirwa serivisi z'ubuvuzi ni ukugira ngo hakurweho mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara no kwirinda kuzikwirakwiza.
Ikinyamakuru cyandika ku buzima kitwa "The New England Journal of Medicine" gitangaza ko gukaraba intoki mu mavuriro bikiri ingorabahizi, aho usanga umubare munini w'abaganga n'abaforomo bakunze kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi; ibi bikaba bituma udukoko twanduza indwara dukwirakwira.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'ubundi buryo bworoshye bishobora kugabanya ikigero cy'indwara zandurira mu nzira y'amaraso ku kigero cya 66%. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryashyize ahagaragara inyandiko igaragaza uburyo bwizewe bwo gukaraba intoki no gukoresha imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Umushinga w'amabwiriza y'isuku y'intoki atangwa n'ikigo ashobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwacyo kugira ngo abantu bayatangeho ibitekerezo.
Ivugurura ry'ingenzi ryakozwe na Whitby n'abandi.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'intoki, niba hasabwe kugaragaza ibisabwa n'amabwiriza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rigena "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo kugira aho uhurira n'amaraso/amatembabuzi
mbere y'igikorwa cyo kuvura, na
nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.Kongera imiti yica indwara ku isabune (amasabune "akoreshwa nk'imiti" cyangwa "ayica mikorobe") bituma gukaraba intoki bidufasha kwica udukoko twanduza.
Ubwo buryo bwo kwica mikorobe, bushobora gukenerwa mbere yo kubaga cyangwa ahantu higanje cyane ibinyabuzima bihangana n'imiti irwanya indwara.Kugira ngo ukube intoki neza mbere yo kubaga, ni ngombwa kugira robine ishobora gufungwa no gufungurwa udakoresheje intoki, umuti w'isuku wa chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, igitambaro gifite isuku cyo kumutsa intoki nyuma yo kuzikaraba, ndetse n'uburoso bufite isuku bwo gukuba intoki ndetse n'ikindi gikoresho gifite isuku cyo gusukura inzara zo ku ntoki.
Ugomba kwiyambura imitako yose.
Ubu buryo busaba gukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, akenshi hagati y'iminota 2 kugeza kuri 6.
Gukuba intoki igihe kirekire(iminota 10) si ngombwa.
Mu gihe uri gutosa amaboko, irinde ko amazi ari ku maboko yongera kumanukira ku ntoki.
Nyuma yo kurangiza gukaraba intoki, zihanaguze igitambaro gisukuye maze wambare umwambaro wo mu cyumba cy'imbagwa.
Mu rwego rwo kugabanya udukoko twanduza, ni byiza gukaraba intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti woza intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Mu bugenzuzi bwakorewe ibitaro bivura indwara ziterwa n'udukoko twitwa "sitafilokoke", byagaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi iva mu gusukura intoki ituruka muri 20% ya mbere yo gukaraba, naho inyungu nkeya yiyongeraho ikaboneka iyo inshuro zo gusukura intoki zongerewe kugera hejuru ya 35%.
Gukaraba ukoresheje isabune isanzwe bitanga umusaruro urenze inshuro eshatu mu kigero cy'indwara ziterwa n'udukoko two mu biribwa ugerereranyije no gukaraba ukoresheje isabune yagenewe kwica udukoko twandura. Iyo ugerereranyije gukoresha umuti basiga mu ntoki n'isabune yagenewe kwica udukoko twandura mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30, byose byagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki bigabanya kwandura udukoko ku kigero cya 26% ugerereranyije n'isabune yagenewe kwica udukoko twandura.
Ariko gukaraba ukoresheje isabune n'amazi ni byo byiza kurusha gukoresha imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki mu rwego rwo kugabanya virusi y'ibicurane bya A/H1N1 n'utundi dukoko dufite ubukana dusigara mu ntoki. Ibikorwa byo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu mavuriro bishobora kubamo no kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera imiti yifashishwa mu gusukura intoki no kubyibutsa abakozi mu buryo bwanditse ndetse no mu magambo.
Hakenewe gukorwa ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza uburyo ubu bufasha ari ingirakamaro cyane mu kwita ku buzima ahantu henshi hatandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifatwa nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi kandi buhendutse bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza, ndetse n'imirire myiza.
Nyamara, kutabona amazi ku buryo buhoraho, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho bifasha mu gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, ku mashuri n'aho abantu bakorera ni imbogamizi ikomeye ituma kugira imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ku bantu bose bitagerwaho.
Dutanze urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, robine zo gukarabiraho intoki ziri hafi y'ubwiherero rusange cyangwa bw'abantu ku giti cyabo ziracyari nkeya, nubwo hari ubundi buryo buhendutse bwo kubaka ahantu ho gukarabira intoki.
Ariko, umubare muto w’abakaraba intoki unashobora guterwa n’umuco wabaye karande wo kudakaraba aho guterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere no gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune bishobora kugira icyo bihindura mu gufata ingamba, gutuma abantu bamenya ibyiza byo gukaraba intoki bikanatuma abaturage bahindura imyitwarire by’igihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibi bikorwe mu buryo bunoze, kubikurikirana no kubisuzuma ni ngombwa.
Isuzuma ry’ubushakashatsi 70 ryasanze uburyo bushingiye ku baturage butanga umusaruro mu kongera ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki muri LMICs, mu gihe kumenyekanisha ibikorwa ku mbuga nkoranyambaga bidatanga umusaruro. Urugero rumwe ni aho guteza imbere ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ari "Uburyo bwahawe inyenyeri eshatu" na UNICEF mu gushishikariza amashuri gukoresha uburyo bworoheje, budahenze mu guharanira ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, hamwe n’ibindi bikoresho by’isuku.
Iyo ibipimo by’ibanze bigezweho, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe akagera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka aho abantu bakarabira intoki bishobora kuba bumwe mu buryo bw’ubukangurambaga bwo guteza imbere umuco wo gukaraba intoki bukorwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n’impfu z’abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw’ubukangurambaga bwo gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kugera ku ntego zo guhindura imyitwarire. Bitewe n’icyorezo cya koronavirusi cyo mu 2019-20, UNICEF yateje imbere emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwagaragaje muri rusange umusaruro wo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y’amajyambere bigereranyijwe n’igipimo cya DALYs.
Cyakora, isuzuma rimwe rigaragaza ko guteza imbere umuco wo gukaraba intoki n’isabune byatanze umusaruro kurusha ibindi bikorwa byo gukoresha amazi n’isukura.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki mu buzima bwa muntu; by’umwihariko, abantu bafite intege nke nk’ababyeyi bakimara kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomerekeye ku rugamba bari mu bitaro, kagaragaye hagati mu kinyejana cya 19 kagaragajwe n’abantu babiri batangije isuku yo mu ntoki: Umuganga w’umunyahongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Viyene, muri Otirishe na Florence Nightingale, umwongerezakazi "watangije uburyo bushya bwo gukora umwuga w’ubuforomo".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bakibwira ko indwara zandura ziterwa n’impumuro mbi yitwa miyazima.
Muri za 1980, ibyorezo biterwa n’ibiribwa n’ubwandu bushamikiye ku buvuzi bwatumye Ikigo cya CDC cy’Amerika kirushaho kongera imbaraga mu gukangurira abantu kugira isuku yo mu ntoki nk’uburyo bw’ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry’indwara.
Icyorezo cy’ibicurane by’ingurube cyo mu 2009 n’icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyo mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu birushaho gusobanukirwa neza akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n’isabune mu kwirinda kwandura izo ndwara zandura.
Urugero, inyandiko nini zanditseho "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" zamanitswe iruhande rwa ravabo zo gukarabiramo intoki mu bwiherero rusange bw’inyubako z’ibiro n’ibibuga by’indege mu Budage.
Ijambo "gukaraba intoki" ku kintu runaka, bisobanura ubushake buke bw’umuntu bwo kutemera ibyo yakoze cyangwa kutemera ubugambanyi muri icyo gikorwa.
Byakomotse mu Gitabo cyo muri Bibiliya cya Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yakarabye intoki ze amaze gufata icyemezo cyo kubamba Yezu Kristu, ariko iyo nteruro ikomeza gukoreshwa cyane mu bavuga ururimi rw’Icyongereza.
Mu ikinamico ya Macbeth yanditswe na Shakespeare, Madamazera Macbeth yatangiye kujya akaraba intoki ze mu rwego rwo gukuraho ikizinga yatekerezaga ko afite, bigaragaza ko umutima wamukomangaga ku bw’ibyaha yakoze n’ibyo yatumye umugabo we akora.
Byagaragaye ko abantu, iyo bamaze kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza gukora ibikorwa bidakwiye, bagerageza gukaraba intoki inshuro nyinshi kurusha abandi, no guha agaciro ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki kurusha ibindi.
Kandi, abemererwa gukaraba intoki bamaze gutekereza ibyo bikorwa bibi bakunda kutongera gukora ibindi bikorwa byo "kwisukura" bihana nko gukora ibikorwa by’ubukorerabushake.
Hari amadini asaba ko abayoboke bayo bakaraba intoki mu rwego rw’isuku no kugaragaza imigenzo y’idini. Gukaraba intoki hagaragazwa imigenzo y’idini, hakoreshejwe amazi gusa nta sabune ukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bigize umuco uranga amadini menshi atandukanye, harimo ababahayi, abahindu, abatevira n’abanetirati yadayimu mu Idini rya Kiyahudi, ravabo mu bemera Yezu, na wudu muri Isiramu. Amadini anasaba abayoboke bayo kugira isuku bakaraba intoki, cyane cyane nyuma yo gukora ibikorwa byihariye.
Abahindu, Idini rya Kiyahudi na Isiramu bategeka gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kuva mu bwiherero.
Kandi Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Idini rya Kiyahudi na Isiramu bategeka gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma ya buri gufata amafunguro.
Ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 ahakorerwa akazi
Ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 ahakorerwa akazi ni zo za ngombwa mu gushaka umutekano n’ubuzima bwiza ahakorerwa akazi mu rwego rwo kwirinda indwara ya koronavirusi yo mu 2019 (COVID-19).
Ingamba nziza zo kurwanya icyorezo ahakorerwa akazi ziterwa n’aho abantu bakorera n’akazi bakora, hashingiwe ku isesengurangaruka ry’ahashobora guturuka indwara, ubukana bw’indwara mu baturage n’ibyago abakozi ku giti cyabo bafite intege nke bafite byo kwandura COVID-19.
Hakurikijwe Urwego rw’Amerika rushinzwe umutekano n’ubuzima bwiza ahakorerwa akazi (OSHA), akazi karimo ibyago bike byo kwandura virusi kaba ari akazi aho abakozi bategerana cyane n’abantu n’abandi bakozi bakorana, aho ingamba z’ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zitegetswe, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo igihe barwaye, amabwiriza yo kwirinda indwara z’ubuhumekero no gukora isuku bihoraho no gutera imiti yica udukuko ahakorerwa akazi.
Akazi karimo ibyago biringaniye byo kwandura virusi kaba ari akazi kagusaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n’abantu hatazwi cyangwa bikekwa ko banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye bitewe ni uko abantu bari kwanduza bagenzi babo cyangwa barakoze ingendo mu mahanga.
Harimo abakozi begerena n’abantu muri rusange nk’abakora mu mashuri, abakorera ahaba hari abantu benshi n’amaduka yakira abakiriya benshi.
Kurwanya icyorezo kuri abo bakozi byiyongera ku mabwiriza y’ibanze yo kurwanya indwara, harimo gutanga umwuka uhagije hakoreshejwe ibyuma biyungurura umwuka, ibikoresho bigukingira iyo witsamuye no kuba hari imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe mu gihe uhuye n’umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
Urwego rwa OSHA rusaba ko abakora mu buvuzi n’uburuhukiro bahuye n’uwanduye cyangwa bikekwa ko yanduye COVID-19 baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bikaba bibongerera ibyago byinshi iyo abo bakozi bakora ibikorwa byo kongerera abarwayi umwuka, gufata cyangwa gusuzuma ibipimo by’umuntu uzwi cyangwa bikekwa ko afite COVID-19.
Uburyo bwiza bwo kurwanya icyorezo kuri abo bakozi harimo gukoresha ibikoresho byabugenewe nk’ibyumba bitageramo umwuka n’imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe ijyanye n’akazi bakora.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ahakorerwa akazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaza ku kazi bitewe no kurwara, bakeneye kwita ku bandi cyangwa bafite ubwoba bwo kuba bakwandura.
Imiterere y’ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka, yaba mu byerekeye uko ibicuruzwa bitumizwa n’uburyo bwo kugura ibyo bicuruzwa (nko guhaha ibicuruzwa mu masaha bitari kugurwa cyane cyangwa serivisi zo kugemura cyangwa gushyikirizwa ibicuruzwa mu modoka).
Hanyuma, kohereza ibicuruzwa bivuye mu duce twashegeshwe n’icyorezo cya COVID-19 bishobora gukomwa mu nkokora. Gahunda yo kwitegura guhangana no kurwanya indwara yandura bishobora kwifashishwa mu bikorwa byo kwirinda.
Gahunda zigaragaza ibyago biri ahantu henshi hakorerwa akazi n’akazi ubwako, harimo aho ushobora kwandura biturutse, ibyago byaturuka mu rugo no mu baturage n’ibyago abakozi bafite ubwabo bitewe n’ubusaza cyangwa kurwara indwara zidakira.
Zinagaragaza imirongo ya ngombwa mu kurwanya indwara hakurwaho ibyo byago n’izindi ngamba zakoreshwa biramutse bitagenze neza mu gihe cy’icyorezo.
Gahunda zo kwitegura no kurwanya indwara yandura zishobora gukurikizwa ku rwego rw’igihugu cyangwa akarere.
Ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo mu bantu runaka harimo kugabanya kwanduzanya hagati y’abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi bitewe n’izindi ndwara barwaye, gukomeza gufungura ibikorwa by’ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka byagira ku bindi bigo mu bikorwa byo gutunganya no kugemura ibicuruzwa.
Ubukana bw’indwara mu baturage aho ibikorwa by’ubucuruzi biherereye bishobora kugira ingaruka ku ngamba zafashwe.
Urukurikirane rw’ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo rukoreshwa cyane mu kurwanya icyorezo harindwa umutekano n’ubuzima bwiza bw’ahakorerwa akazi hakurikijwe umusaruro zitanga.
Aho bidashoboka guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, uburyo butanga umusaruro mu kurwanya icyorezo ni ugukoresha ibikoresho byabugenewe, bigakurikirwa n’ingamba z’ubuyobozi n’imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe.
Kurwanya ubwandu hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byabugenewe ni ukurinda abakozi ibyago bijyanye n’akazi hatagendewe ku myitwarire y’umukozi kandi bishobora kudahenda mu kubishyira mu bikorwa.
Ingamba z’inzego z’ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu mabwiriza agenga akazi cyangwa imikorere bisaba ko bishyirwa mu bikorwa n’umukozi cyangwa umukoresha.
Imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe (PPE) ni yo ifatwa ko idatanga umusaruro cyane nk’izo ngambwa ebyiri zabanje, ariko ishobora gufasha mu kwirinda kuba umuntu yakwandura.
Amoko yose ya PPE agomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku byago umukozi afite, bijyanye neza n’akazi akora (urug.: uduhumekero), kuyambara buri gihe kandi neza, guhora igenzurwa, igafatwa neza inahindurwa uko bibaye ngombwa kandi ikavanwamo, igasukurwa ikabikwa cyangwa ikajugunywa mu kugira ngo hirindwekwandura.
Hakurikijwe ibivugwa n’Urwego rwa OSHA muri Amerika, akazi karimo ibyago bike byo kwandura ni akazi karimo kutegerena cyane n’abantu muri rusange cyangwa n’abo mukorana.
Ingamba z’ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zigomba kubahirizwa n’ahakorerwa akazi hose kandi harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo igihe barwaye, amabwiriza yo kwirinda indwara z’ubuhumekero harimo kwipfuka igihe ukoroye cyangwa witsamuye, gutanga udutumbaro tw’isuku n’aho tujugunywa habugenewe, gutegura guhanahana amakuru hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga, kwirinda ko abakozi basimburanwa ku kazi binjirira cyangwa basohokera rimwe niba bikenewe, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho bya bagenzi babo no gusukura no gutera umuti wica udukoko kenshi ahakorerwa akazi.
Guhita umenya ukanashyira mu kato abantu bashobora kuba banduye ni igikorwa cy’ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasura n’abandi bari ahakorerwa akazi.
Ikigo cya CDC cyo muri Amerika gisaba ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by’indwara y’ubuhumekero ikaze baguma mu rugo kugeza batagifite umuriro, ibimenyetso by’umuriro n’ibindi bimenyetso byibuze bakamara amasaha 24 badakoresheje imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ivura ibimenyetso bafite no koroshya ingamba zo gusaba ikiruhuko cy’uburwayi, guha uruhushya abakozi bakaguma mu rugo hari uwo mu muryango wabo urwaye no kumenyesha abakozi iby’izo ngamba.
Ku bw’Urwego rwa OSHA, akazi karimo ibyago biringaniye byo kwandura virusi ni akazi kagusaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana mu ntera itageze muri m 1,8 n’abantu hatazwi cyangwa bikekwa ko banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba barwaye virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 bitewe no kwanduzanya hagati y’abantu bari ahakorerwa ibikorwa by’ubucuruzi cyangwa kubera ko abantu baherutse gukorera ingendo ahantu harangwa ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Harimo abakozi bakunda kwegerana n’abantu muri rusange nk’abakora mu mashuri, abakorera ahaba hari abantu benshi n’amaduka yakira abakiriya benshi. Kurwanya ubwandu hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byabugenewe kuri aba bakozi n’andi matsinda afite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo ibyuma biyungurura umwuka, kongera umubare w’ibyuma bitanga umwuka, no gushyiraho ibigaragaza aho umuntu atarenga nk’ibikoze muri purasitike bigukingira iyo witsamuye no gushyiraho idirishya rigenewe abakiriya bahaha batavuye mu modoka. Ingamba z’ubuyobozi mu kurwanya ubwandu muri aba bakozi n’andi matsinda y’abakozi afite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo gushishikariza abakozi barwaye kuguma mu rugo, guhindura inama zabaga imbonankubone zikaba hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga, kwirinda ko abakozi basimburanwa ku kazi binjirira cyangwa basohokera icyarimwe, guhagarika ingendo zitari ngombwa ujya ahari icyorezo cya COVID-19, gushyiraho gahunda yo guhanahana amakuru mu buryo bwihutirwa harimo ihuriro risubiza impungenge z’abakozi, guha abakozi ubumenyi bugezweho n’amahugurwa ku byago byo kwandura no kwirinda COVID-19, guhugura abakozi bakeneye gukoresha imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe, ubaha ibikoresho n’aho gukorera habafasha kugira isuku bwite isaba gukaraba intoki kenshi, kugabanya umubare w’abakiriya n’abagera ahantu rusange ku kazi no gushyiraho ibyapa bikangurira abantu gukaraba intoki n’izindi ngamba zo kwirinda COVID-19. Bitewe n’akazi, abakozi byibuze bafite ibyago biringaniye byo kwandura virusi bashobora kwambara imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe harimo kwambarira icyarimwe uturindantoki, ikanzu, masike cyangwa agapfukamunwa cyangwa amataratara.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry’abafite ibyago basabwa gake gukoresha agahumekero.
Iyo umuntu arwaye ari mu ndege, hagomba gushyirwaho ingamba ziboneye zo kurinda abakozi n’abandi bagenzi harimo gushyira umurwayi ahawenyine ntakomeze kuba hamwe n’abandi agasigamo intera ya metero 2, hagashyirwaho ukora mu ndege umwe akaba ari we uha umurwayi ibyo akeneye, kumuha agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusabai kwipfuka umunwa n’amazuru akoresheje udutambaro igihe akoroye cyangwa yitsamuye.
Abakora mu ndege bagomba kwambara uturindantoki two kwa muganga dutabwa tumaze gukoreshwa igihe bari gufasha umurwayi uri mu ndege cyangwa gukora ku matembabuzi yo mu mubiri cyangwa gukora ahantu hashobora kuba handuye no kwambara imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe igihe ari ngombwa iyo umurwayi uri mu ndege afite umuriro, inkorora y’akayi cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Uturindantoki n’ibindi bikoresho bitabwa bimaze gukoreshwa bigomba gushyirwa mu ishashi yabugenewe kandi ahantu handuye hagomba guhanagurwa no guterwa umuti wica udukoko nyuma yo kuhakoresha. Ku mato atwara abagenzi, harimo n’amato atembereza ba mukerarugendo n’andi mato atwara abagenzi, kurwanya virusi harimo gusubika ingendo igihe hari urwaye no kwishyira mu kato no kubimenyesha ivuriro ryo mu bwato ako kanya iyo hari umuntu ugize umuriro cyangwa ugaragaje ibindi bimenyetso ari mu bwato.
Ibyiza ni uko yakurikiranwa n’abaganga igihe uwo muntu yashyizwe mu cyumba cya wenyine. Ku bigo by’amashuri n’amarerero, Ikigo cya CDC gisaba ko afungwa by’igihe gito kugira ngo asukurwe cyangwa aterwemo umuti wica udukoko igihe umuntu wanduye agaragaye mu nyubako y’ishuri hatitwawe ku kuba umuntu yanduza mugenzi we.
Nubwo haba hari umubare muto cyangwa munini wo kwanduzanya hagati y’abantu, ingamba zo kwirinda kwegerana zishobora gukurikizwa hahagarikwa ingendoshuri n’amateraniro y’abantu benshi nk’imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amasomo yo kuririmba muri korari cyangwa gufatira amafunguro muri kantine, kongera umwanya hagati y’intebe n’indi, gusiga umwanya hari uwinjiye cyangwa usohotse, kureka ibyo gusura bitari ngombwa no gukoresha ivuriro riri ahandi ku bana bagaragaza ibimenyetso bimeze nk’iby’ibicurane.
Iyo hari ukwanduzanya mu baturage bo mu gace runaka, usibye ingamba zo kwirinda kwegerana gufunga amashuri igihe kirekire bishobora gutekerezwaho. Ku bakora mu nzego z’umutekano bakora buri munsi akazi gahoraho, ibyago byo kwandura ako kanya ni bike hakurikijwe ibitangazwa n’Ikigo cya CDC.
Abashinzwe umutekano bahuye n’umuntu byemejwe ko yanduye cyangwa bikekwa ko afite COVID-19 basabwa kubahiriza amabwiriza amwe nk’ay’abaganga bakora aho bikomeye, harimo kwambara imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe.
Iyo habayeho kwegerana mu gihe cyo gufata umuntu, abakozi bagomba guhanagura no gutera umuti wica udukuko imikandara baba bambaye n’ibikoresho byabo mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje imiti ihanagura ikoreshwa mu rugo cyangwa udutambaro duhanagura no gukurikiza amabwiriza asanzwe yo kubika no guta imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe yakoreshejwe no kubika no kumesa imyenda.
Urwego rwa OSHA rusaba ko bamwe mu bakora mu nzego z’ubuzima n’uburuhukiro bari mu byiciro byo hejuru cyangwa hejuru cyane byo kuba bafite ibyago byo kwandura.
Akazi karimo ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo abakora mu buvuzi, muri raboratwari, n’abatwara abagiye cyangwa bavuye kwa muganga bashobora kuba bahuye n’umuntu bizwi ko arwaye cyangwa bikweka ko arwaye COVID-19.
Abo baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyo abakora ako kazi bakora ibikorwa birimo kongerera abarwayi umwuka, gufata cyangwa gusuzuma ibipimo by’umuntu bizwi ko arwaye cyangwa bikekwa ko arwaye COVID-19.
Ibikorwa byo kongerera abarwayi umwuka harimo kumushyira uduheha mu mubiri, gutuma akorora, kumushyiramo uduheha ahumekeramo, bumwe mu buvuzi bw’amenyo no kuyasuzuma cyangwa gufata ibipimo by’imbere mu mubiri.
Ibyago byinshi byo kwandurira mu buruhukiro bifitwe n’abakozi bategura imibiri y’abantu bazwiho cyangwa bikekwa ko banduye COVID-19 ubwo bapfaga; bagira ibyago biri hejuru igihe bakora ibizamini byo kureba ikishe umuntu. Kandi kurwanya ubwandu hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byabugenewe harimo amatsinda y’ibyago hakubiyemo ibyumba by’akato ku barwayi bazwiho kurwara cyangwa bakekwaho kurwara COVID-19, harimo gukora ibikorwa byo kongerera umwuka abarwayi.
Igikoresho gitanga umwuka cyihariye gishobora kuba kiboneye kuri bamwe mu bavuzi n’abakora mu buruhukiro.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu rwego rwa 3 rw’umutekano wo kwa muganga.
OMS isaba ko abarwayi baza mu bitaro bashyirwa ukwabo aho bategerereza bitewe no kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. Kandi yaba imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe, Urwego rwa OSHA rusaba gukoresha uduhumekero ku bakorera mu ntera itageze muri metero 2 y’abazwiho kurwara cyangwa bikekwa ko barwaye, banduye virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 n’abakora ibikorwa byo kongerera umwuka abarwayi.
Muri Amerika, uduhumekero twemejwe n’Urwego rwa NIOSH two mu bwoko bwa N95 cyangwa utwiza kurushaho tugomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe gahunda iboneye, yanditse yo kwirinda hakoreshejwe uduhumekero harimo gusuzuma ko gakwiye ukambara, guhugurwa uko kambarwa n’ibizamini byo kwa muganga.
Ubundi bwoko bw’uduhumekero dushobora kurinda utwambaye neza kurushaho no gutuma umukozi yumva yisanzuye kurushaho. OMS ntisaba ko abakozi bambara amakanzu kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y’ubuhumekero aho kuba ari indwara yandura binyuze mu matembabuzi y’umubiri.
OMS isaba ko hambarwa gusa udupfukamunwa two kwa muganga ku bakozi bakira abagana ibigo bitandukanye.
Ku bafata ibipimo byo mu myanya y’ubuhumekero, abita ku barwayi, cyangwa abatwara abarwayi ba COVID-19 batabongerera umwuka, OMS isaba ko bambara agapfukamunwa ko kwa muganga, amataratara cyangwa kasike, ikanzu n’uturindantoki.
Iyo hakozwe igikorwa cyo kongerera umwuka umurwayi, agapfukamunwa ko kwa muganga gasimburwa n’uduhumekero twa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Bitewe ni uko kugemura imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe (PPE) bidahagije ku isi, OMS isaba ko hagabanywa ibituma hakenerwa imyenda y’ubwirinzi yabugenewe hagakoreshwa ubuvuzi bw’iyakure, gushyiraho ibituma abantu bategerena nk’amadirishya abonerana, no gutuma abatanga ubuvuzi butaziguye ari bo bonyine binjira mu cyumba kirimo umurwayi wa COVID-19, gukoresha PPE igihe ari ngombwa gusa mu kazi kihariye, gukomeza gukoresha agahumekero kamwe nta kukavanamo igihe uri kwita ku barwayi benshi barwaye kimwe, kubakurikirana no guhuza ibikorwa byo gukora no kugemura PPE no kubuza ikoreshwa ry’udupfukamunwa ku batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
